Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.77,0:00:49.98,Default,,0,0,0,,你心里应该清楚吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.61,0:00:54.40,Default,,0,0,0,,杀了慎二的人是谁
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.66,0:01:04.41,Default,,0,0,0,,看来想清楚了 不再骗自己了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.50,0:01:12.34,Default,,0,0,0,,那东西成长到如今的地步 再想毁掉已经没这么容易了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.01,0:01:18.26,Default,,0,0,0,,我本来是想利用你背叛她的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.64,0:01:21.26,Default,,0,0,0,,还好做了另一手准备
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.72,0:01:23.73,Default,,0,0,0,,你说准备
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.39,0:01:27.98,Default,,0,0,0,,她现在还能保持人形 只能称得上是半成品
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.48,0:01:32.90,Default,,0,0,0,,但即使如此 这小子也是立了大功
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.28,0:01:36.99,Default,,0,0,0,,脏砚
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.70,0:01:38.82,Default,,0,0,0,,樱人在哪里
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.33,0:01:48.67,Default,,0,0,0,,当姐姐是什么感觉
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.06,0:02:12.69,Default,,0,0,0,,我要感谢你
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.98,0:02:16.32,Default,,0,0,0,,那孩子任何事都只会忍耐
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.78,0:02:22.78,Default,,0,0,0,,是你教会她什么是欲望 让她渴望占有他人
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.49,0:02:28.04,Default,,0,0,0,,现在她杀了自己的兄长 已经没人能停止她的脚步了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.94,0:02:33.29,Default,,0,0,0,,她会将爱因兹贝伦吸收的Archer的灵魂
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.88,0:02:38.59,Default,,0,0,0,,还有前往门的钥匙统统抢走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.59,0:02:41.30,Default,,0,0,0,,脏砚
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.74,0:03:01.11,Default,,0,0,0,,来吧 接受那个黑影吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.61,0:03:03.28,Default,,0,0,0,,樱
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.37,0:03:10.58,Default,,0,0,0,,好的 爷爷
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.01,0:03:23.97,Default,,0,0,0,,樱
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.07,0:03:42.07,Default,,0,0,0,,原来姐姐在家啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.11,0:03:46.16,Default,,0,0,0,,毕竟 我没有士郎的动机
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.16,0:03:48.08,Default,,0,0,0,,不会像他一样跑去救你
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.04,0:03:52.79,Default,,0,0,0,,更何况我很明白 你迟早会打伊莉雅的主意
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.00,0:03:57.00,Default,,0,0,0,,真伤人啊 姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.80,0:04:00.67,Default,,0,0,0,,我有这么坏吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.38,0:04:02.59,Default,,0,0,0,,这还用问
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.38,0:04:09.27,Default,,0,0,0,,你最终还是背叛了想要保护间桐樱的人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.64,0:04:13.81,Default,,0,0,0,,没有错
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.77,0:04:16.81,Default,,0,0,0,,过去是这样
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.69,0:04:20.94,Default,,0,0,0,,但现在我不弱小了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.49,0:04:25.20,Default,,0,0,0,,所以该换我来保护前辈了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.95,0:04:27.78,Default,,0,0,0,,因为
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.58,0:04:31.41,Default,,0,0,0,,现在的我 比他更强
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.62,0:04:35.67,Default,,0,0,0,,调和
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.62,0:04:35.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Verschmelzen
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.17,0:04:39.50,Default,,0,0,0,,这可不行
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.55,0:04:44.76,Default,,0,0,0,,要是用了这种魔术
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.76,0:04:47.93,Default,,0,0,0,,房子不就被你弄坏了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.86,0:05:11.29,Default,,0,0,0,,真美味 这就是姐姐的魔力
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.75,0:05:14.41,Default,,0,0,0,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.46,0:05:18.04,Default,,0,0,0,,只是这样…还不够
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.75,0:05:22.46,Default,,0,0,0,,姐姐…还会站起来
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.38,0:05:25.05,Default,,0,0,0,,因为…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.97,0:05:28.72,Default,,0,0,0,,姐姐是…英雄啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.27,0:05:41.94,Default,,0,0,0,,樱
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.90,0:05:46.86,Default,,0,0,0,,前…辈…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.58,0:05:56.25,Default,,0,0,0,,远坂
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.46,0:06:00.71,Default,,0,0,0,,这是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.47,0:06:09.80,Default,,0,0,0,,为什么你要护着姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.89,0:06:13.93,Default,,0,0,0,,为什么对我视而不见
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.14,0:06:17.02,Default,,0,0,0,,为什么不骂我
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.02,0:06:21.36,Default,,0,0,0,,你明明看到哥哥都变成那样了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.69,0:06:24.98,Default,,0,0,0,,不对 那是脏砚的…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.98,0:06:25.99,Default,,0,0,0,,不是的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.15,0:06:29.20,Default,,0,0,0,,你看 前辈
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.78,0:06:33.99,Default,,0,0,0,,我从一开始就坏掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.95,0:06:36.54,Default,,0,0,0,,樱…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.71,0:06:39.79,Default,,0,0,0,,和我在一起很痛苦吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.63,0:06:45.05,Default,,0,0,0,,所以我才必须从你面前消失
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.05,0:06:47.42,Default,,0,0,0,,但是我做不到
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.80,0:06:52.55,Default,,0,0,0,,因为对我而言 只有前辈你才是唯一的快乐
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.68,0:06:56.18,Default,,0,0,0,,而你也无法离开我
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.85,0:06:59.89,Default,,0,0,0,,因为你无法背叛自己
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.40,0:07:10.95,Default,,0,0,0,,所以 我会杀了你
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.95,0:07:13.41,Default,,0,0,0,,为了让你不再痛苦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.20,0:07:16.29,Default,,0,0,0,,为了让你能永远留在我身边
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.17,0:07:29.26,Default,,0,0,0,,这是你的命令 樱
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.51,0:07:33.43,Default,,0,0,0,,你让我不管什么情况都要保护好卫宫士郎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.51,0:07:38.22,Default,,0,0,0,,真不听话啊 Rider
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.85,0:07:45.48,Default,,0,0,0,,樱 你不能去那个地方
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.44,0:07:47.82,Default,,0,0,0,,那里一无所有
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.57,0:07:51.74,Default,,0,0,0,,只有黑暗和孤独
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.49,0:07:57.58,Default,,0,0,0,,我是为了阻止你 才出现在了这里…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.51,0:08:17.89,Default,,0,0,0,,樱
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.81,0:08:26.81,Default,,0,0,0,,你的使命就到此为止了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.32,0:08:36.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Rider 我会吸收你
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.32,0:08:37.95,Default,,0,0,0,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.95,0:08:42.75,Default,,0,0,0,,虽然你已经没用了 但是我会特别让你变成Saber一样
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.29,0:08:50.17,Default,,0,0,0,,到此为止了 樱
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.30,0:08:54.72,Default,,0,0,0,,我跟你走
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.55,0:08:56.34,Default,,0,0,0,,伊莉雅
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.55,0:08:59.01,Default,,0,0,0,,你疯了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.22,0:09:02.98,Default,,0,0,0,,你会死的你知道吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.98,0:09:05.69,Default,,0,0,0,,反正抵抗也没用吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.56,0:09:09.36,Default,,0,0,0,,在这里你是最强的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.23,0:09:15.20,Default,,0,0,0,,我是…最强的…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.12,0:09:24.33,Default,,0,0,0,,最后的钥匙不在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.91,0:09:28.04,Default,,0,0,0,,如果你想作为后继者把门打开
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.75,0:09:30.88,Default,,0,0,0,,就要先去我的城堡取钥匙
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.30,0:09:37.38,Default,,0,0,0,,好吧 我就信你一回
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.19,0:09:52.19,Default,,0,0,0,,不要再跟过来了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.32,0:09:55.49,Default,,0,0,0,,下次我就只能下杀手了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.78,0:09:59.53,Default,,0,0,0,,那我走了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.49,0:10:04.08,Default,,0,0,0,,这段时间我很开心 大哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.43,0:10:20.22,Default,,0,0,0,,让开 Saber
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.89,0:10:22.64,Default,,0,0,0,,现在的你能做什么
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.56,0:10:27.23,Default,,0,0,0,,无论以何种形式樱都会得到圣杯
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.98,0:10:30.32,Default,,0,0,0,,哪怕其结果是她的死亡
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.61,0:10:33.73,Default,,0,0,0,,这也是拯救间桐樱的唯一出路
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.78,0:10:38.07,Default,,0,0,0,,这是我最后的忠告
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.07,0:10:41.03,Default,,0,0,0,,如果你还是执意要追上来
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.03,0:10:44.45,Default,,0,0,0,,到那个时候 我就会斩下你的人头
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.61,0:11:14.86,Default,,0,0,0,,胜负已定
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.11,0:11:24.53,Default,,0,0,0,,不 那种事早在久远的过去就被注定了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.37,0:11:27.58,Default,,0,0,0,,扭曲的圣杯战争
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.45,0:11:30.50,Default,,0,0,0,,本来独一无二的圣杯
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.92,0:11:35.04,Default,,0,0,0,,现在这里出现了第二个
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.34,0:11:39.84,Default,,0,0,0,,而且其容器也很适合作为圣杯
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.38,0:11:43.47,Default,,0,0,0,,准确来说 是其内在适合
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.72,0:11:47.04,Default,,0,0,0,,如果容器不合适
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.04,0:11:50.35,Default,,0,0,0,,那就只能沦为会增殖的肉块
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.81,0:11:53.48,Default,,0,0,0,,舞台已经准备好了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.44,0:11:56.61,Default,,0,0,0,,解答之物
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.11,0:11:59.19,Default,,0,0,0,,就要诞生了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.70,0:12:06.49,Default,,0,0,0,,如果有些东西在观众席上看不见
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.91,0:12:12.79,Default,,0,0,0,,那么我也站上舞台吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.21,0:12:20.13,Default,,0,0,0,,言峰
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.09,0:12:21.97,Default,,0,0,0,,救救…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.97,0:12:23.72,Default,,0,0,0,,远坂…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.90,0:13:18.81,Default,,0,0,0,,醒了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.78,0:13:21.32,Default,,0,0,0,,身体能动了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.07,0:13:24.99,Default,,0,0,0,,言峰
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.45,0:13:28.16,Default,,0,0,0,,远坂呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.41,0:13:33.25,Default,,0,0,0,,她比你更加虚弱
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.58,0:13:36.83,Default,,0,0,0,,我把她埋进了远坂家的庭院里
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.74,0:13:40.34,Default,,0,0,0,,埋？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.25,0:13:44.88,Default,,0,0,0,,明早应该就会变回那个盛气凌人的样子吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.88,0:13:47.80,Default,,0,0,0,,那就好
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.93,0:13:50.10,Default,,0,0,0,,给你添麻烦了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.89,0:13:52.10,Default,,0,0,0,,我得走了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.60,0:13:55.48,Default,,0,0,0,,你要去哪里
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.56,0:14:00.31,Default,,0,0,0,,伊莉雅为了保护我们
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.23,0:14:02.65,Default,,0,0,0,,跟樱走了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.73,0:14:04.28,Default,,0,0,0,,所以
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.49,0:14:07.07,Default,,0,0,0,,间桐樱变成了敌人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.65,0:14:09.11,Default,,0,0,0,,对吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.00,0:14:21.09,Default,,0,0,0,,跟我来
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.92,0:14:31.14,Default,,0,0,0,,间桐脏砚的目的 应该是转移到成为空壳的樱身上
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.47,0:14:31.85,Default,,0,0,0,,什…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.97,0:14:35.93,Default,,0,0,0,,也就是说 夺回伊莉雅斯菲尔
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.93,0:14:40.69,Default,,0,0,0,,抢在樱变成空壳之前打倒脏砚
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.86,0:14:45.82,Default,,0,0,0,,到这里为止 我们的目的是相同的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.44,0:14:47.82,Default,,0,0,0,,目的…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.62,0:14:58.91,Default,,0,0,0,,我是说 我可以协助你
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.75,0:15:07.46,Default,,0,0,0,,对了 Rider呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.72,0:15:12.89,Default,,0,0,0,,放弃吧 她们之间的魔术回路应该还连着
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.01,0:15:17.22,Default,,0,0,0,,还没等靠近城堡就被发现就得不偿失了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.11,0:15:33.12,anotation,,0,0,0,,昨晚
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.12,0:15:35.91,anotation,,0,0,0,,关于冬木市发生的失踪事件
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.24,0:15:40.12,anotation,,0,0,0,,被害者的人数及原因目前仍在调查中
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.71,0:15:45.67,anotation,,0,0,0,,与此同时 在新都站前一带发生的大规模停电…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.55,0:15:48.01,Default,,0,0,0,,如果是那个男人的话
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.34,0:15:52.01,Default,,0,0,0,,应该会在间桐樱变成这样之前就把她杀了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.39,0:15:59.18,Default,,0,0,0,,你的父亲是个可以为了所谓的正义
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.18,0:16:02.64,Default,,0,0,0,,舍弃一切感情的男人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.65,0:16:08.03,Default,,0,0,0,,卫宫切嗣 他为人处世的方式让我很不快
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.98,0:16:12.32,Default,,0,0,0,,他会舍弃一切开始就拥有的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.32,0:16:15.53,Default,,0,0,0,,而我从开始就一无所有
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.45,0:16:21.04,Default,,0,0,0,,虽然结果殊途同归 但其过程却大相径庭
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.91,0:16:25.38,Default,,0,0,0,,这点正是我和他决定性的区别
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.46,0:16:29.63,Default,,0,0,0,,既然要舍弃 当初为何要拥有
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.34,0:16:33.09,Default,,0,0,0,,然而他却一直背负着
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.09,0:16:37.10,Default,,0,0,0,,甚至在舍弃之后再次捡起
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.18,0:16:39.06,Default,,0,0,0,,真是个…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.85,0:16:41.73,Default,,0,0,0,,幸福的男人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.85,0:16:46.19,Default,,0,0,0,,切嗣…很幸福？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.86,0:16:50.50,Default,,0,0,0,,他爱自己 爱身边的人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.50,0:16:55.61,Default,,0,0,0,,原谅罪恶 接受惩罚 抚养生命健康成长
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.57,0:17:00.24,Default,,0,0,0,,你们称之为幸福的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.74,0:17:03.54,Default,,0,0,0,,无法给我带来喜悦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.21,0:17:06.17,Default,,0,0,0,,我想说的只有这个
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.71,0:17:16.30,Default,,0,0,0,,你那时候为什么会救樱
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.18,0:17:19.01,Default,,0,0,0,,人迟早都会死
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.93,0:17:22.52,Default,,0,0,0,,如果当时死的只有她
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.68,0:17:26.77,Default,,0,0,0,,我也不会想方设法去救她
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.36,0:17:34.49,Default,,0,0,0,,我祝福的 是即将从间桐樱体内诞生的黑暗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.40,0:17:36.66,Default,,0,0,0,,你说那个黑影？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.53,0:17:39.91,Default,,0,0,0,,那东西…不是只会杀人吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.95,0:17:43.08,Default,,0,0,0,,然而它尚未诞生
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.91,0:17:45.75,Default,,0,0,0,,倘若它出生了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.75,0:17:48.71,Default,,0,0,0,,那么罪恶也好 惩罚也好 它都理应被问责
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.50,0:17:51.42,Default,,0,0,0,,但这不能成为扼杀它的理由
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.59,0:17:57.51,Default,,0,0,0,,还是你要说 罪犯的孩子出生前就是罪犯吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.14,0:18:00.39,Default,,0,0,0,,因而你就要杀了他吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.56,0:18:10.56,Default,,0,0,0,,换我问你一个问题
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.48,0:18:13.98,Default,,0,0,0,,间桐樱
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.86,0:18:18.28,Default,,0,0,0,,现在的她毫无疑问就是个食人魔
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.03,0:18:24.20,Default,,0,0,0,,即使如此 你也要庇护她吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.96,0:18:33.84,Default,,0,0,0,,她杀了许多人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.17,0:18:38.59,Default,,0,0,0,,我不认为她会就这么原谅自己
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.94,0:18:43.60,Default,,0,0,0,,既然是这样 杀了她对她而言难道不是一种解脱吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.39,0:18:47.64,Default,,0,0,0,,这样还能为那些被她杀了的人赎罪
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.35,0:18:51.02,Default,,0,0,0,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.31,0:18:53.94,Default,,0,0,0,,这不是偿还
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.61,0:18:56.78,Default,,0,0,0,,这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.15,0:19:02.66,Default,,0,0,0,,也就是说你不打算走卫宫切嗣的道路吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.57,0:19:36.48,Default,,0,0,0,,我调查一下
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.20,0:19:45.78,Default,,0,0,0,,同调 开始
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.95,0:19:48.87,Default,,0,0,0,,基本骨架…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.16,0:19:50.83,Default,,0,0,0,,解明
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.92,0:19:53.04,Default,,0,0,0,,构成材质…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.00,0:19:54.67,Default,,0,0,0,,解明
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.88,0:19:59.92,Default,,0,0,0,,在三楼…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.63,0:20:03.09,Default,,0,0,0,,最左边的房间…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.48,0:20:12.39,Default,,0,0,0,,樱…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.56,0:20:15.65,Default,,0,0,0,,到此为止了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.90,0:20:19.15,Default,,0,0,0,,别搞错优先顺序
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.61,0:20:22.70,Default,,0,0,0,,我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.74,0:20:25.87,Default,,0,0,0,,那么 卫宫士郎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.84,0:20:30.37,Default,,0,0,0,,你有爬山的经验吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.82,0:20:42.17,Default,,0,0,0,,真的要为了那些人准备正装吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.51,0:20:44.43,Default,,0,0,0,,你们忘了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.14,0:20:49.10,Default,,0,0,0,,我们的使命就是完成圣杯
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.68,0:20:54.31,Default,,0,0,0,,只要容器合适 是不是我并不重要
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.52,0:21:35.14,Default,,0,0,0,,谁会把人往窗子扔啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.85,0:21:43.61,Default,,0,0,0,,我只是看你单手贴着墙爬的样子太可怜了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.82,0:21:45.61,Default,,0,0,0,,你们是谁
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.24,0:21:46.91,Default,,0,0,0,,贼人
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.60,0:21:50.58,Default,,0,0,0,,不是的 我们是…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.70,0:21:52.45,Default,,0,0,0,,士郎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.96,0:21:57.37,Default,,0,0,0,,伊莉雅
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.37,0:21:58.21,Default,,0,0,0,,你来干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.80,0:22:01.71,Default,,0,0,0,,回去
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.00,0:22:05.01,Default,,0,0,0,,你已经没有出场的必要了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.74,0:22:09.47,Default,,0,0,0,,樱就交给我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.22,0:22:11.85,Default,,0,0,0,,这就是…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.97,0:22:14.60,Default,,0,0,0,,我的使命
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.73,0:22:18.73,Default,,0,0,0,,笨蛋伊莉雅
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.65,0:22:27.40,Default,,0,0,0,,干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.99,0:22:30.03,Default,,0,0,0,,无所谓
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.41,0:22:35.54,Default,,0,0,0,,我不管你的使命是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.20,0:22:39.75,Default,,0,0,0,,你再怎么逞强 再怎么强装没事
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.25,0:22:41.88,Default,,0,0,0,,也别想骗过我的眼睛
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.42,0:22:45.09,Default,,0,0,0,,谁逞强了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.51,0:22:46.92,Default,,0,0,0,,我就是圣杯
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.92,0:22:48.88,Default,,0,0,0,,这就叫逞强 笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.47,0:22:50.80,Default,,0,0,0,,你就是你
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.39,0:22:56.85,Default,,0,0,0,,别随便为了他人去牺牲自己
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.73,0:23:01.65,Default,,0,0,0,,也不看看…你自己
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.20,0:23:12.87,Default,,0,0,0,,伊莉雅
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.50,0:23:19.37,Default,,0,0,0,,这种事…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.00,0:23:22.79,Default,,0,0,0,,哪有想的这么好
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.13,0:23:30.18,Default,,0,0,0,,你们还有工夫谈天说地
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.18,0:23:32.59,Default,,0,0,0,,喂 放我下来
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.47,0:23:34.10,Default,,0,0,0,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.31,0:23:38.48,Default,,0,0,0,,这里是我们的城堡 不必担心
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.27,0:23:40.89,Default,,0,0,0,,伊莉雅就拜托了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.94,0:23:50.70,Default,,0,0,0,,士郎
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.86,0:23:56.58,Default,,0,0,0,,那种高度不用魔术就纵身跃下 实在令人生畏
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.45,0:23:58.50,Default,,0,0,0,,不想活了？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.00,0:24:02.08,Default,,0,0,0,,要你管 我还以为能行的
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.08,0:24:04.54,Default,,0,0,0,,咦
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.92,0:24:07.88,Default,,0,0,0,,被Archer拉了一把吗
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.80,0:24:16.35,Default,,0,0,0,,你来了
Dialogue: 0,0:24:17.35,0:24:18.26,Default,,0,0,0,,前辈
Dialogue: 0,0:24:36.74,0:24:37.16,Default,,0,0,0,,什…
Dialogue: 0,0:24:38.03,0:24:38.79,Default,,0,0,0,,快走
Dialogue: 0,0:24:48.50,0:24:49.30,Default,,0,0,0,,好快
Dialogue: 0,0:24:50.96,0:24:51.51,Default,,0,0,0,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:24:52.47,0:24:53.34,Default,,0,0,0,,既然如此
Dialogue: 0,0:24:59.76,0:25:00.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Berserker
Dialogue: 0,0:25:47.44,0:25:50.52,Default,,0,0,0,,看来不是普通的人偶吗
Dialogue: 0,0:25:56.15,0:25:57.28,Default,,0,0,0,,带她走
Dialogue: 0,0:26:01.12,0:26:01.91,Default,,0,0,0,,卫宫
Dialogue: 0,0:26:02.70,0:26:05.33,Default,,0,0,0,,如果你要救的是女人 那就别让她死
Dialogue: 0,0:26:06.50,0:26:11.59,Default,,0,0,0,,看着她在眼前被杀害 可不是件好受的事
Dialogue: 0,0:26:17.43,0:26:18.47,Default,,0,0,0,,我们走 伊莉雅
Dialogue: 0,0:26:29.10,0:26:31.19,Default,,0,0,0,,我是不会放走纯白圣杯的
Dialogue: 0,0:26:32.07,0:26:35.53,Default,,0,0,0,,我也有必须实现的愿望
Dialogue: 0,0:26:47.71,0:26:49.12,Default,,0,0,0,,它在看我？
Dialogue: 0,0:27:01.01,0:27:01.59,Default,,0,0,0,,士郎
Dialogue: 0,0:27:02.54,0:27:03.93,Default,,0,0,0,,放下我 离开这里
Dialogue: 0,0:27:05.14,0:27:06.22,Default,,0,0,0,,我怎么可能…
Dialogue: 0,0:27:36.50,0:27:39.51,Default,,0,0,0,,真是狼狈啊 绮礼
Dialogue: 0,0:27:40.84,0:27:42.26,Default,,0,0,0,,间桐脏砚
Dialogue: 0,0:27:44.10,0:27:48.10,Default,,0,0,0,,这样啊 你主动找上门来了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:27:49.92,0:27:51.19,Default,,0,0,0,,舞台落幕了
Dialogue: 0,0:27:52.02,0:27:55.48,Default,,0,0,0,,给他个痛快 Assassin
Dialogue: 0,0:28:04.20,0:28:06.70,Default,,0,0,0,,虽然不是现在才回想起来
Dialogue: 0,0:28:07.70,0:28:10.62,Default,,0,0,0,,我生来就就有缺陷
Dialogue: 0,0:28:11.46,0:28:14.71,Default,,0,0,0,,幸福对我而言只有痛苦
Dialogue: 0,0:28:15.17,0:28:17.21,Default,,0,0,0,,只有绝望才能为我带来真正的喜悦
Dialogue: 0,0:28:18.38,0:28:25.26,Default,,0,0,0,,我深知自己是一种恶的存在
Dialogue: 0,0:28:26.51,0:28:28.10,Default,,0,0,0,,真是无可救药的缺陷
Dialogue: 0,0:28:29.31,0:28:32.73,Default,,0,0,0,,身为恶人却具备良知
Dialogue: 0,0:28:35.31,0:28:38.86,Default,,0,0,0,,我也曾努力去矫正自己
Dialogue: 0,0:28:40.11,0:28:44.86,Default,,0,0,0,,我最后的一次尝试 是去爱一个女人
Dialogue: 0,0:28:54.79,0:28:56.17,Default,,0,0,0,,准确来说
Dialogue: 0,0:28:56.17,0:29:01.42,Default,,0,0,0,,我希望自己能够爱上她 生儿育女
Dialogue: 0,0:29:02.51,0:29:03.88,Default,,0,0,0,,而结果
Dialogue: 0,0:29:06.26,0:29:07.26,Default,,0,0,0,,我还是…
Dialogue: 0,0:29:08.28,0:29:10.01,Default,,0,0,0,,无法爱上你
Dialogue: 0,0:29:12.10,0:29:12.77,Default,,0,0,0,,不
Dialogue: 0,0:29:13.81,0:29:16.19,Default,,0,0,0,,你是爱我的
Dialogue: 0,0:29:29.83,0:29:30.74,Default,,0,0,0,,宝具——
Dialogue: 0,0:29:32.95,0:29:34.25,Default,,0,0,0,,妄想心音
Dialogue: 0,0:29:32.95,0:29:34.25,small,,0,0,0,,Zabaniya
Dialogue: 0,0:29:41.80,0:29:42.96,Default,,0,0,0,,结束了
Dialogue: 0,0:29:51.31,0:29:52.85,Default,,0,0,0,,混蛋…你该不会…
Dialogue: 0,0:30:12.20,0:30:13.16,Default,,0,0,0,,宣告
Dialogue: 0,0:30:15.25,0:30:18.33,Default,,0,0,0,,我既杀灭 我亦创生
Dialogue: 0,0:30:18.33,0:30:21.13,Default,,0,0,0,,我既伤害 我亦济世
Dialogue: 0,0:30:21.79,0:30:25.21,Default,,0,0,0,,人皆于我手 不可逃
Dialogue: 0,0:30:25.21,0:30:28.01,Default,,0,0,0,,人皆于我眼 不可遁
Dialogue: 0,0:30:26.88,0:30:29.30,up,,0,0,0,,混蛋 你这家伙…
Dialogue: 0,0:30:29.59,0:30:30.93,Default,,0,0,0,,回归尘土吧
Dialogue: 0,0:30:31.51,0:30:34.93,Default,,0,0,0,,败走者 衰老者 为我所召
Dialogue: 0,0:30:35.31,0:30:39.85,Default,,0,0,0,,委身于我 师法于我 效忠于我
Dialogue: 0,0:30:39.85,0:30:41.11,Default,,0,0,0,,赐汝安息
Dialogue: 0,0:30:41.11,0:30:43.69,Default,,0,0,0,,毋忘歌颂 毋忘祈祷
Dialogue: 0,0:30:43.69,0:30:45.03,Default,,0,0,0,,毋忘我名
Dialogue: 0,0:30:45.53,0:30:49.32,Default,,0,0,0,,我身为轻 解放汝于万物之重苦
Dialogue: 0,0:30:49.91,0:30:52.28,Default,,0,0,0,,原来你想杀了我
Dialogue: 0,0:30:52.53,0:30:54.54,Default,,0,0,0,,安息于我手
Dialogue: 0,0:30:54.99,0:30:58.71,Default,,0,0,0,,燃烧汝罪 刻于烙印
Dialogue: 0,0:30:59.21,0:31:04.05,Default,,0,0,0,,永恒不灭唯死所赐
Dialogue: 0,0:31:05.13,0:31:06.72,Default,,0,0,0,,宽恕在此
Dialogue: 0,0:31:06.72,0:31:09.34,Default,,0,0,0,,受肉之我在此宣誓
Dialogue: 0,0:31:09.76,0:31:11.26,Default,,0,0,0,,这样又能改变什么
Dialogue: 0,0:31:11.26,0:31:13.43,Default,,0,0,0,,没人能救赎你
Dialogue: 0,0:31:14.64,0:31:16.35,Default,,0,0,0,,愿主怜此哀魂
Dialogue: 0,0:31:14.64,0:31:16.35,small,,0,0,0,,Kyrie Eleison
Dialogue: 0,0:31:33.37,0:31:37.58,Default,,0,0,0,,用圣经的圣言直接攻击灵体吗
Dialogue: 0,0:31:40.74,0:31:44.63,Default,,0,0,0,,对魔术师阁下而言真可谓是天敌
Dialogue: 0,0:31:46.59,0:31:47.80,Default,,0,0,0,,而且你…
Dialogue: 0,0:31:50.09,0:31:52.05,Default,,0,0,0,,看样子早就遭到污染了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:31:56.60,0:31:58.31,Default,,0,0,0,,是我失算了
Dialogue: 0,0:32:11.03,0:32:11.61,Default,,0,0,0,,看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:32:12.45,0:32:14.82,Default,,0,0,0,,你哭了
Dialogue: 0,0:32:17.54,0:32:19.33,Default,,0,0,0,,那是误会
Dialogue: 0,0:32:23.17,0:32:25.50,Default,,0,0,0,,那时候我确实感受到了痛心
Dialogue: 0,0:32:26.46,0:32:29.01,Default,,0,0,0,,但那不是为了那个女人的死
Dialogue: 0,0:32:33.97,0:32:35.76,Default,,0,0,0,,既然无论如何难免一死
Dialogue: 0,0:32:36.80,0:32:39.18,Default,,0,0,0,,我更希望能亲自动手
Dialogue: 0,0:32:52.53,0:32:53.45,Default,,0,0,0,,士郎
Dialogue: 0,0:32:54.53,0:32:56.57,Default,,0,0,0,,你没事吧 伊莉雅
Dialogue: 0,0:33:04.92,0:33:06.42,Default,,0,0,0,,士郎 快逃
Dialogue: 0,0:33:06.88,0:33:08.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Berserker正在找我
Dialogue: 0,0:33:10.17,0:33:11.17,Default,,0,0,0,,士郎
Dialogue: 0,0:33:17.80,0:33:19.97,Default,,0,0,0,,哥哥就该保护好妹妹
Dialogue: 0,0:33:21.56,0:33:22.27,Default,,0,0,0,,可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:33:23.77,0:33:24.56,Default,,0,0,0,,别说了
Dialogue: 0,0:33:25.14,0:33:27.61,Default,,0,0,0,,你既然叫了我哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:33:27.61,0:33:28.52,Default,,0,0,0,,我就是你哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:33:30.23,0:33:30.86,Default,,0,0,0,,即便是…
Dialogue: 0,0:33:31.44,0:33:32.94,Default,,0,0,0,,没有血缘相连
Dialogue: 0,0:33:43.00,0:33:43.75,Default,,0,0,0,,士郎
Dialogue: 0,0:33:44.29,0:33:46.08,Default,,0,0,0,,你如果用了Archer的手臂
Dialogue: 0,0:33:46.42,0:33:47.50,Default,,0,0,0,,就再也回不去了
Dialogue: 0,0:33:50.96,0:33:52.13,Default,,0,0,0,,你会死的
Dialogue: 0,0:33:53.05,0:33:53.76,Default,,0,0,0,,不
Dialogue: 0,0:33:55.80,0:33:57.72,Default,,0,0,0,,就是为了要活下去才用它
Dialogue: 0,0:33:59.80,0:34:00.64,Default,,0,0,0,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:34:01.93,0:34:04.73,Default,,0,0,0,,为什么你要做到这个地步
Dialogue: 0,0:34:05.35,0:34:09.02,Default,,0,0,0,,你又没做什么坏事
Dialogue: 0,0:34:13.57,0:34:14.11,Default,,0,0,0,,不
Dialogue: 0,0:34:15.07,0:34:17.82,Default,,0,0,0,,至今为止 我做过不少坏事
Dialogue: 0,0:34:19.24,0:34:19.74,Default,,0,0,0,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:34:21.70,0:34:22.54,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢你
Dialogue: 0,0:34:29.67,0:34:31.60,Default,,0,0,0,,我不知道用了这只手臂
Dialogue: 0,0:34:31.60,0:34:32.92,Default,,0,0,0,,会发生什么
Dialogue: 0,0:34:33.92,0:34:35.92,Default,,0,0,0,,想要保护樱的誓言也好
Dialogue: 0,0:34:36.47,0:34:38.43,Default,,0,0,0,,将伊莉雅带回去的决心也好
Dialogue: 0,0:34:39.30,0:34:42.76,Default,,0,0,0,,甚至其他所有事 可能都会再也想不起来
Dialogue: 0,0:34:43.86,0:34:44.47,Default,,0,0,0,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:34:45.43,0:34:47.10,Default,,0,0,0,,那家伙是认为我用得上
Dialogue: 0,0:34:47.35,0:34:48.94,Default,,0,0,0,,才将这只手臂托付给了我
Dialogue: 0,0:34:52.44,0:34:53.57,Default,,0,0,0,,我可以打倒它吧
Dialogue: 0,0:34:54.19,0:34:54.90,Default,,0,0,0,,伊莉雅
Dialogue: 0,0:35:18.92,0:35:20.26,Default,,0,0,0,,身体和意识都…
Dialogue: 0,0:35:21.05,0:35:22.64,Default,,0,0,0,,无知觉地分崩离析
Dialogue: 0,0:35:25.51,0:35:27.48,Default,,0,0,0,,为什么我会在这里…
Dialogue: 0,0:35:30.19,0:35:32.86,Default,,0,0,0,,又为什么 会变成这样
Dialogue: 0,0:35:34.65,0:35:36.86,Default,,0,0,0,,我是为了什么而战
Dialogue: 0,0:35:59.01,0:36:00.17,Default,,0,0,0,,你能跟上来吗
Dialogue: 0,0:36:10.94,0:36:14.73,Default,,0,0,0,,不是我要跟上你
Dialogue: 0,0:36:15.52,0:36:17.69,Default,,0,0,0,,而是你这家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:36:27.14,0:36:29.56,Default,,0,0,0,,给我跟上来
Dialogue: 0,0:36:46.93,0:36:48.89,Default,,0,0,0,,投影 开始
Dialogue: 0,0:36:46.93,0:36:48.89,small,,0,0,0,,Trace On
Dialogue: 0,0:37:09.95,0:37:12.46,Default,,0,0,0,,投影 装填
Dialogue: 0,0:37:09.95,0:37:12.46,small,,0,0,0,,Trigger Off
Dialogue: 0,0:37:27.01,0:37:30.43,Default,,0,0,0,,是·射杀百头
Dialogue: 0,0:37:27.01,0:37:30.43,small,,0,0,0,,Nine Lives Blade Works
Dialogue: 0,0:38:36.21,0:38:37.92,Default,,0,0,0,,由你来守护
Dialogue: 0,0:38:58.85,0:38:59.77,Default,,0,0,0,,士郎
Dialogue: 0,0:39:09.86,0:39:10.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Saber
Dialogue: 0,0:39:23.63,0:39:24.71,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:39:25.67,0:39:28.72,Default,,0,0,0,,心脏被揪住有什么感想
Dialogue: 0,0:39:34.47,0:39:38.06,Default,,0,0,0,,神父 你在十年前就已经死了
Dialogue: 0,0:39:39.06,0:39:41.23,Default,,0,0,0,,你能苟延残喘至今的原因
Dialogue: 0,0:39:41.90,0:39:43.02,Default,,0,0,0,,我想想…
Dialogue: 0,0:39:43.69,0:39:45.07,Default,,0,0,0,,应该是之前被我吃掉的…
Dialogue: 0,0:39:45.94,0:39:49.28,Default,,0,0,0,,那个金色的人沐浴了圣杯的内容物
Dialogue: 0,0:39:50.16,0:39:52.82,Default,,0,0,0,,但他又无法被污染
Dialogue: 0,0:39:52.82,0:39:55.74,Default,,0,0,0,,所以就流向身为御主的你
Dialogue: 0,0:39:56.20,0:39:57.16,Default,,0,0,0,,我说的没错吧
Dialogue: 0,0:39:58.91,0:40:01.87,Default,,0,0,0,,你变了 间桐樱
Dialogue: 0,0:40:03.21,0:40:05.25,Default,,0,0,0,,是的 我变了
Dialogue: 0,0:40:06.59,0:40:10.55,Default,,0,0,0,,我已经不再是曾经的间桐樱了
Dialogue: 0,0:40:12.05,0:40:13.55,Default,,0,0,0,,那么软弱的女孩
Dialogue: 0,0:40:14.04,0:40:15.39,Default,,0,0,0,,已经不存在了
Dialogue: 0,0:40:19.85,0:40:21.52,Default,,0,0,0,,你无须隐瞒
Dialogue: 0,0:40:22.85,0:40:24.77,Default,,0,0,0,,隐瞒…什么
Dialogue: 0,0:40:25.06,0:40:27.52,Default,,0,0,0,,这并非是你的另一面
Dialogue: 0,0:40:28.32,0:40:32.99,Default,,0,0,0,,如今沉醉于暴力的人 也是间桐樱
Dialogue: 0,0:40:35.64,0:40:37.91,Default,,0,0,0,,明明是你把我变成这个样子的
Dialogue: 0,0:40:39.54,0:40:40.62,Default,,0,0,0,,我不否认
Dialogue: 0,0:40:41.46,0:40:43.58,Default,,0,0,0,,我救了你
Dialogue: 0,0:40:44.75,0:40:50.76,Default,,0,0,0,,而你也如我所望 顺利地在让Avenger诞生
Dialogue: 0,0:40:51.84,0:40:53.13,Default,,0,0,0,,简直易如反掌
Dialogue: 0,0:40:56.89,0:40:58.35,Default,,0,0,0,,才不是易如反掌
Dialogue: 0,0:40:59.28,0:41:02.77,Default,,0,0,0,,你根本不知道我有多么痛苦
Dialogue: 0,0:41:03.31,0:41:06.23,Default,,0,0,0,,不知道 也没有必要知道
Dialogue: 0,0:41:33.51,0:41:35.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Berserker
Dialogue: 0,0:41:36.59,0:41:37.22,Default,,0,0,0,,不要…
Dialogue: 0,0:41:37.76,0:41:39.30,Default,,0,0,0,,不要进来
Dialogue: 0,0:41:49.82,0:41:50.90,Default,,0,0,0,,你很走运
Dialogue: 0,0:41:51.73,0:41:53.86,Default,,0,0,0,,樱在叫我
Dialogue: 0,0:41:58.24,0:41:58.74,Default,,0,0,0,,不
Dialogue: 0,0:41:59.53,0:42:03.16,Default,,0,0,0,,这不是运 而是你以一己之力…
Dialogue: 0,0:42:04.37,0:42:05.25,Default,,0,0,0,,获得的胜利吗
Dialogue: 0,0:42:15.09,0:42:15.84,Default,,0,0,0,,士郎
Dialogue: 0,0:42:18.51,0:42:19.30,Default,,0,0,0,,士郎
Dialogue: 0,0:42:22.51,0:42:23.43,Default,,0,0,0,,我没事
Dialogue: 0,0:42:25.98,0:42:27.23,Default,,0,0,0,,我没事的
Dialogue: 0,0:42:28.69,0:42:29.40,Default,,0,0,0,,我们回去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:43:30.75,0:43:32.54,Default,,0,0,0,,是用了手臂的关系吗
Dialogue: 0,0:43:42.47,0:43:44.47,Default,,0,0,0,,睡醒了吗 士郎
Dialogue: 0,0:43:45.10,0:43:45.89,Default,,0,0,0,,远坂
Dialogue: 0,0:43:46.72,0:43:47.89,Default,,0,0,0,,你没事了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:43:49.43,0:43:53.27,Default,,0,0,0,,跟你比起来 那是当然
Dialogue: 0,0:43:56.73,0:43:58.69,Default,,0,0,0,,总之你没事就好
Dialogue: 0,0:44:00.74,0:44:01.45,Default,,0,0,0,,那是…
Dialogue: 0,0:44:04.42,0:44:05.24,Default,,0,0,0,,这是…
Dialogue: 0,0:44:07.20,0:44:08.62,Default,,0,0,0,,很重要的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:44:11.12,0:44:13.29,Default,,0,0,0,,我必须一直带在身边
Dialogue: 0,0:44:17.50,0:44:19.88,Default,,0,0,0,,我刚才说了什么
Dialogue: 0,0:44:21.09,0:44:24.34,Default,,0,0,0,,那上面还残留了一点魔力
Dialogue: 0,0:44:24.98,0:44:25.68,Default,,0,0,0,,带着它吧
Dialogue: 0,0:44:26.81,0:44:29.02,Default,,0,0,0,,或许会派上什么用场
Dialogue: 0,0:44:35.52,0:44:37.23,Default,,0,0,0,,那就准备一下
Dialogue: 0,0:44:37.90,0:44:38.98,Default,,0,0,0,,我们要出门了
Dialogue: 0,0:44:49.45,0:44:53.04,Default,,0,0,0,,我只会对参与圣杯战争的最后一位御主
Dialogue: 0,0:44:53.04,0:44:55.00,Default,,0,0,0,,说出这个事实
Dialogue: 0,0:44:56.71,0:44:58.63,Default,,0,0,0,,我接下来要说的
Dialogue: 0,0:44:58.63,0:45:00.21,Default,,0,0,0,,是我们的核心
Dialogue: 0,0:45:00.98,0:45:01.55,Default,,0,0,0,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:45:02.63,0:45:05.01,Default,,0,0,0,,这不是你们该背负的
Dialogue: 0,0:45:07.43,0:45:09.47,Default,,0,0,0,,所谓的圣杯战争
Dialogue: 0,0:45:09.47,0:45:11.80,Default,,0,0,0,,是召唤出七位英灵
Dialogue: 0,0:45:11.80,0:45:14.56,Default,,0,0,0,,让他们相互残杀以决定圣杯的所有权
Dialogue: 0,0:45:16.02,0:45:19.36,Default,,0,0,0,,不过那只是表面上的规则
Dialogue: 0,0:45:21.53,0:45:22.11,Default,,0,0,0,,没错
Dialogue: 0,0:45:23.07,0:45:26.78,Default,,0,0,0,,御主充其量只是将从者召唤至现世的媒介
Dialogue: 0,0:45:27.99,0:45:31.95,Default,,0,0,0,,完成圣杯 需要的只是英灵
Dialogue: 0,0:45:33.46,0:45:35.12,Default,,0,0,0,,他们的灵魂
Dialogue: 0,0:45:35.12,0:45:38.25,Default,,0,0,0,,将由爱因兹贝伦准备的圣杯回收
Dialogue: 0,0:45:38.88,0:45:41.80,Default,,0,0,0,,作为启动大圣杯的炉心
Dialogue: 0,0:45:44.13,0:45:45.38,Default,,0,0,0,,大圣杯？
Dialogue: 0,0:45:46.30,0:45:48.97,Default,,0,0,0,,就是远坂家管辖地上的魔法阵
Dialogue: 0,0:45:50.18,0:45:53.35,Default,,0,0,0,,圣杯战争的系统都由它来管理
Dialogue: 0,0:45:55.23,0:45:57.31,Default,,0,0,0,,事情发生在三百年前
Dialogue: 0,0:45:58.19,0:45:59.86,Default,,0,0,0,,爱因兹贝伦、玛奇里
Dialogue: 0,0:46:00.15,0:46:01.65,Default,,0,0,0,,还有远坂 这御三家
Dialogue: 0,0:46:02.40,0:46:05.65,Default,,0,0,0,,企图利用圣杯去外界
Dialogue: 0,0:46:06.86,0:46:08.57,Default,,0,0,0,,这才是他们真正的目的
Dialogue: 0,0:46:10.16,0:46:13.45,Default,,0,0,0,,爱因兹贝伦失传的秘辛
Dialogue: 0,0:46:13.45,0:46:16.33,Default,,0,0,0,,能够实现真正不老不死的大仪式
Dialogue: 0,0:46:17.25,0:46:18.29,Default,,0,0,0,,天之杯——
Dialogue: 0,0:46:19.17,0:46:20.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Heaven's Feel
Dialogue: 0,0:46:21.46,0:46:23.55,Default,,0,0,0,,能将灵魂物质化的魔法
Dialogue: 0,0:46:28.51,0:46:32.22,Default,,0,0,0,,我接下来要说的 跟你们也有关系
Dialogue: 0,0:46:34.35,0:46:35.64,Default,,0,0,0,,是樱的事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:46:36.27,0:46:37.06,Default,,0,0,0,,告诉我
Dialogue: 0,0:46:37.52,0:46:39.40,Default,,0,0,0,,樱的身上究竟发生了什么
Dialogue: 0,0:46:40.69,0:46:45.61,Default,,0,0,0,,脏砚将樱变成现在这副模样 他想要得到的
Dialogue: 0,0:46:46.78,0:46:48.66,Default,,0,0,0,,就是复仇者
Dialogue: 0,0:46:46.78,0:46:48.66,small,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1015,995)}Avenger
Dialogue: 0,0:46:50.37,0:46:53.04,Default,,0,0,0,,那是圣杯战争中的第八职阶
Dialogue: 0,0:46:54.04,0:46:57.54,Default,,0,0,0,,和樱同化后投射出来的黑影的本体
Dialogue: 0,0:46:59.00,0:46:59.88,Default,,0,0,0,,安哥拉·曼纽
Dialogue: 0,0:46:59.00,0:46:59.88,small,,0,0,0,, Angra·Mainyu
Dialogue: 0,0:47:02.29,0:47:06.05,Default,,0,0,0,,这是发生在某个信奉拜火教村落的故事
Dialogue: 0,0:47:07.47,0:47:08.55,Default,,0,0,0,,那些人一直在想
Dialogue: 0,0:47:09.47,0:47:12.26,Default,,0,0,0,,是否能将人类从万恶中解放出来
Dialogue: 0,0:47:13.26,0:47:16.14,Default,,0,0,0,,过上正直且正确的生活
Dialogue: 0,0:47:17.18,0:47:21.44,Default,,0,0,0,,然后他们选出了一位青年
Dialogue: 0,0:47:22.56,0:47:25.65,Default,,0,0,0,,让他背负这世界上所有的罪恶
Dialogue: 0,0:47:26.78,0:47:28.11,Default,,0,0,0,,他们想借此证明
Dialogue: 0,0:47:28.11,0:47:31.62,Default,,0,0,0,,除他以外 其他所有人都是善良的
Dialogue: 0,0:47:33.12,0:47:33.95,Default,,0,0,0,,就这样
Dialogue: 0,0:47:34.83,0:47:37.08,Default,,0,0,0,,一位英雄诞生了
Dialogue: 0,0:47:38.71,0:47:40.62,Default,,0,0,0,,他以罪恶的化身为世人所憎恶
Dialogue: 0,0:47:41.33,0:47:46.00,Default,,0,0,0,,碌碌无名的他 却同时又被当作神来崇拜
Dialogue: 0,0:47:47.55,0:47:48.92,Default,,0,0,0,,这就是反英雄
Dialogue: 0,0:47:49.88,0:47:50.76,Default,,0,0,0,,安哥拉·曼纽
Dialogue: 0,0:47:53.18,0:47:54.72,Default,,0,0,0,,在第三次的圣杯战争中
Dialogue: 0,0:47:55.39,0:47:58.93,Default,,0,0,0,,爱因兹贝伦将他以从者的身份召唤了出来
Dialogue: 0,0:48:00.39,0:48:03.06,Default,,0,0,0,,但是他太弱小了
Dialogue: 0,0:48:04.40,0:48:08.40,Default,,0,0,0,,他在战争前期就被打败 被圣杯吸收
Dialogue: 0,0:48:10.40,0:48:11.36,Default,,0,0,0,,那时
Dialogue: 0,0:48:12.28,0:48:16.66,Default,,0,0,0,,圣杯允诺了一个愿望
Dialogue: 0,0:48:18.75,0:48:22.79,Default,,0,0,0,,“希望他背负人世间所有罪恶”
Dialogue: 0,0:48:24.04,0:48:28.21,Default,,0,0,0,,这个愿望终于在圣杯中得以实现
Dialogue: 0,0:48:29.63,0:48:32.01,Default,,0,0,0,,呈现世界所有恶的他
Dialogue: 0,0:48:32.68,0:48:36.47,Default,,0,0,0,,成为了能够诅咒全世界60亿人口的存在
Dialogue: 0,0:48:37.81,0:48:38.56,Default,,0,0,0,,这就是…
Dialogue: 0,0:48:39.77,0:48:41.43,Default,,0,0,0,,那个黑影的本体
Dialogue: 0,0:48:45.15,0:48:49.11,Default,,0,0,0,,切嗣在上次的圣杯战争中破坏了圣杯
Dialogue: 0,0:48:51.11,0:48:55.24,Default,,0,0,0,,安哥拉曼纽在切嗣果决的行动下没有出生
Dialogue: 0,0:48:55.95,0:48:58.08,Default,,0,0,0,,就这样被留在了大圣杯之中
Dialogue: 0,0:48:59.79,0:49:02.50,Default,,0,0,0,,它的一部分由言峰接收下来
Dialogue: 0,0:49:03.42,0:49:07.29,Default,,0,0,0,,脏砚将圣杯内部的碎片植入人体
Dialogue: 0,0:49:07.29,0:49:09.42,Default,,0,0,0,,以此造出的人造圣杯
Dialogue: 0,0:49:10.46,0:49:11.30,Default,,0,0,0,,就是樱
Dialogue: 0,0:49:12.92,0:49:14.68,Default,,0,0,0,,无论安哥拉曼纽是怎样的存在
Dialogue: 0,0:49:15.14,0:49:17.39,Default,,0,0,0,,它都是从者
Dialogue: 0,0:49:18.51,0:49:19.14,Default,,0,0,0,,所以
Dialogue: 0,0:49:19.97,0:49:22.66,Default,,0,0,0,,脏砚为了让它服从自己
Dialogue: 0,0:49:22.66,0:49:24.23,Default,,0,0,0,,就让樱成为了它的御主
Dialogue: 0,0:49:27.23,0:49:29.32,Default,,0,0,0,,御主和从者…
Dialogue: 0,0:49:31.42,0:49:33.82,Default,,0,0,0,,时间还有半天不到
Dialogue: 0,0:49:34.91,0:49:36.66,Default,,0,0,0,,它一旦诞生
Dialogue: 0,0:49:37.20,0:49:38.91,Default,,0,0,0,,樱就会彻底改变
Dialogue: 0,0:49:39.58,0:49:41.29,Default,,0,0,0,,任何人都救不了她
Dialogue: 0,0:49:42.12,0:49:43.66,Default,,0,0,0,,也没有人能够获救
Dialogue: 0,0:49:49.04,0:49:54.09,Default,,0,0,0,,所以在前往敌阵之前 我希望士郎能帮我一个忙
Dialogue: 0,0:49:55.80,0:49:59.72,Default,,0,0,0,,老实说 好在你把伊莉雅带了回来
Dialogue: 0,0:50:00.93,0:50:03.77,Default,,0,0,0,,我希望你能和伊莉雅一起
Dialogue: 0,0:50:03.77,0:50:05.64,Default,,0,0,0,,用爱因兹贝伦的记忆
Dialogue: 0,0:50:05.64,0:50:07.94,Default,,0,0,0,,还有流动在这灵脉中土地的记忆
Dialogue: 0,0:50:09.19,0:50:12.98,Default,,0,0,0,,结合两者 投影出宝石剑
Dialogue: 0,0:50:14.69,0:50:15.95,Default,,0,0,0,,宝石剑？
Dialogue: 0,0:50:16.86,0:50:19.78,Default,,0,0,0,,那是远坂家代代相传的秘宝中的秘宝
Dialogue: 0,0:50:21.37,0:50:22.16,Default,,0,0,0,,也是…
Dialogue: 0,0:50:23.62,0:50:26.37,Default,,0,0,0,,用来与樱战斗的武器
Dialogue: 0,0:50:29.50,0:50:30.34,Default,,0,0,0,,我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:50:37.09,0:50:39.30,Default,,0,0,0,,这是以宝石剑为原型的阿佐特剑
Dialogue: 0,0:50:37.09,0:50:39.30,small,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1242,995)}Azoth
Dialogue: 0,0:50:40.05,0:50:42.56,Default,,0,0,0,,其中注入了我十年份的魔力
Dialogue: 0,0:50:43.36,0:50:44.98,Default,,0,0,0,,你用它来辅助投影吧
Dialogue: 0,0:50:50.81,0:50:51.61,Default,,0,0,0,,士郎
Dialogue: 0,0:50:53.02,0:50:55.94,Default,,0,0,0,,说实话 你还能撑多久
Dialogue: 0,0:51:01.32,0:51:02.78,Default,,0,0,0,,我也不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:51:04.70,0:51:08.08,Default,,0,0,0,,但是 活着总有办法的
Dialogue: 0,0:51:15.63,0:51:16.97,Default,,0,0,0,,我没事的
Dialogue: 0,0:51:26.94,0:51:28.23,Default,,0,0,0,,抛除杂念
Dialogue: 0,0:51:28.64,0:51:30.31,Default,,0,0,0,,不要去看无关紧要的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:51:44.91,0:51:45.54,Default,,0,0,0,,大海？
Dialogue: 0,0:51:47.95,0:51:48.62,Default,,0,0,0,,士郎
Dialogue: 0,0:52:03.35,0:52:04.26,Default,,0,0,0,,慎二？
Dialogue: 0,0:52:05.76,0:52:06.26,Default,,0,0,0,,不对
Dialogue: 0,0:52:07.64,0:52:08.52,Default,,0,0,0,,不是这里
Dialogue: 0,0:52:09.43,0:52:10.56,Default,,0,0,0,,去前面吧
Dialogue: 0,0:52:29.75,0:52:30.83,Default,,0,0,0,,就快到了
Dialogue: 0,0:52:31.41,0:52:32.08,Default,,0,0,0,,我们走
Dialogue: 0,0:52:32.67,0:52:33.21,Default,,0,0,0,,那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:52:39.26,0:52:43.93,up,,0,0,0,,为了根绝所有之恶 你们需要奇迹
Dialogue: 0,0:52:42.51,0:52:43.68,Default,,0,0,0,,总算到了
Dialogue: 0,0:52:44.68,0:52:47.47,Default,,0,0,0,,士郎 眼睛不要从他身上离开
Dialogue: 0,0:52:49.68,0:52:51.94,Default,,0,0,0,,相信心中的理念
Dialogue: 0,0:52:52.86,0:52:54.60,Default,,0,0,0,,为了到达根源
Dialogue: 0,0:52:55.06,0:53:01.78,Default,,0,0,0,,远坂、爱因兹贝伦、玛奇里三者将齐心协力开辟道路
Dialogue: 0,0:53:02.74,0:53:05.16,Default,,0,0,0,,你们分别所要提供的是
Dialogue: 0,0:53:06.62,0:53:11.91,Default,,0,0,0,,远坂将提供铺设圣杯的灵地
Dialogue: 0,0:53:12.62,0:53:18.67,Default,,0,0,0,,玛奇里将提供令咒 以束缚用作供品的从者
Dialogue: 0,0:53:19.55,0:53:25.18,Default,,0,0,0,,爱因兹贝伦将提供到达第三魔法的构阵
Dialogue: 0,0:53:27.93,0:53:32.73,Default,,0,0,0,,由我基修亚·泽尔里奇·修拜因奥古来担任见证
Dialogue: 0,0:53:33.94,0:53:35.31,Default,,0,0,0,,那就开始吧
Dialogue: 0,0:54:08.47,0:54:10.56,Default,,0,0,0,,通往根源之门
Dialogue: 0,0:54:12.89,0:54:13.85,Default,,0,0,0,,解放
Dialogue: 0,0:54:26.11,0:54:27.03,Default,,0,0,0,,解放
Dialogue: 0,0:54:32.08,0:54:33.24,Default,,0,0,0,,解放…
Dialogue: 0,0:54:49.51,0:54:50.22,Default,,0,0,0,,士郎
Dialogue: 0,0:55:25.38,0:55:26.97,Default,,0,0,0,,不堪重负了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:55:27.84,0:55:28.93,Default,,0,0,0,,卫宫士郎
Dialogue: 0,0:55:31.47,0:55:32.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Rider
Dialogue: 0,0:55:33.72,0:55:35.77,Default,,0,0,0,,我一直都在监视你
Dialogue: 0,0:55:39.10,0:55:42.61,Default,,0,0,0,,我被赋予的使命是保护好卫宫士郎
Dialogue: 0,0:55:43.27,0:55:46.19,Default,,0,0,0,,但现在你做出了与樱战斗的武器
Dialogue: 0,0:55:49.20,0:55:51.74,Default,,0,0,0,,既然你想对樱不利
Dialogue: 0,0:55:52.74,0:55:54.66,Default,,0,0,0,,那我也没有理由再去保护你
Dialogue: 0,0:55:59.54,0:56:00.33,Default,,0,0,0,,你是…
Dialogue: 0,0:56:01.12,0:56:02.33,Default,,0,0,0,,来杀我的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:56:04.21,0:56:04.92,Default,,0,0,0,,士郎
Dialogue: 0,0:56:05.88,0:56:10.34,Default,,0,0,0,,樱没有通过任何媒介就将我召唤了出来
Dialogue: 0,0:56:12.48,0:56:13.51,Default,,0,0,0,,这种情况
Dialogue: 0,0:56:14.22,0:56:18.02,Default,,0,0,0,,御主会优先召唤出与自己本质接近的从者
Dialogue: 0,0:56:20.10,0:56:20.98,Default,,0,0,0,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:56:21.94,0:56:24.44,Default,,0,0,0,,不希望樱变成怪物
Dialogue: 0,0:56:27.07,0:56:28.53,Default,,0,0,0,,但是 已经…
Dialogue: 0,0:56:31.65,0:56:32.28,Default,,0,0,0,,士郎
Dialogue: 0,0:56:33.24,0:56:35.45,Default,,0,0,0,,既然你要让樱痛苦
Dialogue: 0,0:56:35.87,0:56:37.04,Default,,0,0,0,,这不是为了杀她
Dialogue: 0,0:56:38.70,0:56:40.62,Default,,0,0,0,,而是为了救她
Dialogue: 0,0:56:41.83,0:56:44.42,Default,,0,0,0,,我到最后都会保护樱
Dialogue: 0,0:56:48.30,0:56:51.22,Default,,0,0,0,,不管发生什么事 我都会站在她这边
Dialogue: 0,0:56:52.72,0:56:53.38,Default,,0,0,0,,这是
Dialogue: 0,0:56:54.89,0:56:56.89,Default,,0,0,0,,之前那个问题的…
Dialogue: 0,0:56:58.06,0:56:59.27,Default,,0,0,0,,回答吗
Dialogue: 0,0:57:00.85,0:57:01.68,Default,,0,0,0,,为此
Dialogue: 0,0:57:02.32,0:57:04.19,Default,,0,0,0,,我必须打倒一个人
Dialogue: 0,0:57:05.18,0:57:06.56,Default,,0,0,0,,我需要你的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:57:12.70,0:57:14.53,Default,,0,0,0,,你应该有胜算吧
Dialogue: 0,0:57:18.66,0:57:20.04,Default,,0,0,0,,我明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:57:26.38,0:57:28.34,Default,,0,0,0,,从者 Rider
Dialogue: 0,0:57:29.10,0:57:30.42,Default,,0,0,0,,虽然只是暂时的
Dialogue: 0,0:57:31.01,0:57:36.18,Default,,0,0,0,,我愿化成你的羽翼 前往天际尽头
Dialogue: 0,0:57:53.95,0:57:56.66,Default,,0,0,0,,我还以为你回心转意 想要回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:57:58.49,0:58:00.83,Default,,0,0,0,,居然放了一个影子过来
Dialogue: 0,0:58:00.83,0:58:03.33,Default,,0,0,0,,你学聪明了 樱
Dialogue: 0,0:58:04.62,0:58:05.50,Default,,0,0,0,,姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:58:06.67,0:58:08.79,Default,,0,0,0,,带着前辈逃跑吧
Dialogue: 0,0:58:10.17,0:58:11.46,Default,,0,0,0,,你们走后…
Dialogue: 0,0:58:12.32,0:58:15.38,Default,,0,0,0,,我就与它同归于尽
Dialogue: 0,0:58:18.09,0:58:21.26,Default,,0,0,0,,樱 我先问你
Dialogue: 0,0:58:22.18,0:58:24.56,Default,,0,0,0,,你有打算和安哥拉曼纽断绝关系吗
Dialogue: 0,0:58:29.77,0:58:30.61,Default,,0,0,0,,没有
Dialogue: 0,0:58:31.77,0:58:33.90,Default,,0,0,0,,我好不容易才得到这份力量
Dialogue: 0,0:58:34.74,0:58:36.78,Default,,0,0,0,,我没有离开它的打算
Dialogue: 0,0:58:37.32,0:58:37.99,Default,,0,0,0,,也离不开它
Dialogue: 0,0:58:39.53,0:58:42.41,Default,,0,0,0,,你的意思是 只要我带着士郎走
Dialogue: 0,0:58:42.41,0:58:46.54,Default,,0,0,0,,你就会和安哥拉曼纽同归于尽是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:58:48.76,0:58:51.00,Default,,0,0,0,,是的 所以…
Dialogue: 0,0:58:53.21,0:58:53.96,Default,,0,0,0,,这话
Dialogue: 0,0:58:54.55,0:58:58.30,Default,,0,0,0,,你是搞错了 想说自己快抑制不住了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:59:00.39,0:59:01.22,Default,,0,0,0,,还没发现吗
Dialogue: 0,0:59:02.78,0:59:05.98,Default,,0,0,0,,从刚才开始 你的言行就错得离谱
Dialogue: 0,0:59:06.85,0:59:11.27,Default,,0,0,0,,先说要和它同归于尽 后来又说不想离开它
Dialogue: 0,0:59:17.49,0:59:20.66,Default,,0,0,0,,不用着急 我马上就会去见你的
Dialogue: 0,0:59:22.62,0:59:26.20,Default,,0,0,0,,我会去你那里 确确实实地杀了你
Dialogue: 0,0:59:28.16,0:59:32.59,Default,,0,0,0,,好 我会等你的 姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:59:38.05,0:59:39.51,Default,,0,0,0,,姐姐…
Dialogue: 0,0:59:50.98,0:59:53.44,Default,,0,0,0,,你总算回来了 Assassin
Dialogue: 0,0:59:54.48,0:59:56.82,Default,,0,0,0,,魔术师阁下 您还健在
Dialogue: 0,0:59:57.82,0:59:58.65,Default,,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:59:59.28,1:00:04.12,Default,,0,0,0,,不过现在的我已经没办法提供魔力给你使用了
Dialogue: 0,1:00:05.24,1:00:07.95,Default,,0,0,0,,樱 虽然会加重你的负担
Dialogue: 0,1:00:07.95,1:00:10.46,Default,,0,0,0,,和Assassin签订契约吧
Dialogue: 0,1:00:13.42,1:00:14.38,Default,,0,0,0,,樱
Dialogue: 0,1:00:18.67,1:00:19.67,Default,,0,0,0,,魔术师阁下
Dialogue: 0,1:00:20.74,1:00:21.59,Default,,0,0,0,,这个女人
Dialogue: 0,1:00:22.30,1:00:23.14,Default,,0,0,0,,恐怕已经…
Dialogue: 0,1:00:25.56,1:00:29.27,Default,,0,0,0,,真是干脆而无趣的落幕
Dialogue: 0,1:00:30.48,1:00:33.10,Default,,0,0,0,,那就依照计划 将这个小姑娘
Dialogue: 0,1:00:33.86,1:00:35.65,Default,,0,0,0,,说得真难听
Dialogue: 0,1:00:35.65,1:00:37.90,Default,,0,0,0,,说到底这也是无奈之举
Dialogue: 0,1:00:39.78,1:00:41.36,Default,,0,0,0,,再见了 樱
Dialogue: 0,1:00:42.30,1:00:45.37,Default,,0,0,0,,作为实验品 你能撑到今天
Dialogue: 0,1:00:45.37,1:00:47.95,Default,,0,0,0,,给我带来了不少乐子
Dialogue: 0,1:00:48.79,1:00:50.91,Default,,0,0,0,,没有那个必要
Dialogue: 0,1:01:15.56,1:01:16.81,Default,,0,0,0,,什么嘛
Dialogue: 0,1:01:17.61,1:01:20.40,Default,,0,0,0,,本来就是个没脸的人啊
Dialogue: 0,1:01:22.86,1:01:24.20,Default,,0,0,0,,混…蛋
Dialogue: 0,1:01:25.07,1:01:26.99,Default,,0,0,0,,你什么都不是
Dialogue: 0,1:01:28.33,1:01:30.95,Default,,0,0,0,,别妄想成为真正的血肉之躯
Dialogue: 0,1:01:33.33,1:01:34.37,Default,,0,0,0,,我的…
Dialogue: 0,1:01:35.12,1:01:37.50,Default,,0,0,0,,名…字…
Dialogue: 0,1:01:40.96,1:01:41.42,Default,,0,0,0,,你…
Dialogue: 0,1:01:42.17,1:01:44.47,Default,,0,0,0,,你在干什么 樱
Dialogue: 0,1:01:47.35,1:01:48.64,Default,,0,0,0,,因为爷爷你…
Dialogue: 0,1:01:49.10,1:01:52.77,Default,,0,0,0,,已经不需要他来保护你了吧
Dialogue: 0,1:01:56.73,1:01:57.36,Default,,0,0,0,,什…
Dialogue: 0,1:01:58.19,1:02:00.07,Default,,0,0,0,,我经常在想…
Dialogue: 0,1:02:00.52,1:02:04.03,Default,,0,0,0,,为什么爷爷对我是如此重要的存在
Dialogue: 0,1:02:04.36,1:02:06.74,Default,,0,0,0,,能这样对我为所欲为
Dialogue: 0,1:02:09.45,1:02:11.37,Default,,0,0,0,,现在终于明白了
Dialogue: 0,1:02:16.62,1:02:20.21,Default,,0,0,0,,原来是变成了我神经的一部分啊
Dialogue: 0,1:02:23.42,1:02:27.39,Default,,0,0,0,,我还以为爷爷会更大一点呢
Dialogue: 0,1:02:30.64,1:02:33.18,Default,,0,0,0,,等等 住手 樱
Dialogue: 0,1:02:34.56,1:02:37.35,Default,,0,0,0,,再见了 爷爷
Dialogue: 0,1:02:48.32,1:02:51.16,Default,,0,0,0,,哥哥还有爷爷都不在了
Dialogue: 0,1:02:52.08,1:02:52.91,Default,,0,0,0,,这下…
Dialogue: 0,1:02:54.66,1:02:55.50,Default,,0,0,0,,这下
Dialogue: 0,1:02:57.87,1:02:58.83,Default,,0,0,0,,我…
Dialogue: 0,1:03:02.13,1:03:03.75,Default,,0,0,0,,…该怎么办好呢
Dialogue: 0,1:03:13.10,1:03:13.93,Default,,0,0,0,,还没结束
Dialogue: 0,1:03:15.39,1:03:17.31,Default,,0,0,0,,还有他们在
Dialogue: 0,1:03:19.44,1:03:20.69,Default,,0,0,0,,他们 会来
Dialogue: 0,1:03:25.74,1:03:29.07,Default,,0,0,0,,去 只放姐姐一个人过来
Dialogue: 0,1:03:30.20,1:03:31.24,Default,,0,0,0,,卫宫士郎呢
Dialogue: 0,1:04:32.47,1:04:33.59,Default,,0,0,0,,真是服了自己
Dialogue: 0,1:04:34.39,1:04:35.97,Default,,0,0,0,,没想到在我心中…
Dialogue: 0,1:04:39.81,1:04:42.81,Default,,0,0,0,,樱会这么重要
Dialogue: 0,1:04:48.57,1:04:50.90,Default,,0,0,0,,那就出发吧
Dialogue: 0,1:04:52.15,1:04:52.74,Default,,0,0,0,,凛
Dialogue: 0,1:04:53.70,1:04:54.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Rider
Dialogue: 0,1:04:55.62,1:04:56.37,Default,,0,0,0,,士郎
Dialogue: 0,1:05:01.62,1:05:02.33,Default,,0,0,0,,伊莉雅
Dialogue: 0,1:05:03.58,1:05:05.13,Default,,0,0,0,,等这场战斗结束后
Dialogue: 0,1:05:05.79,1:05:07.71,Default,,0,0,0,,如果你没有去处
Dialogue: 0,1:05:08.80,1:05:10.97,Default,,0,0,0,,要不要就这样住下来
Dialogue: 0,1:05:12.59,1:05:14.34,Default,,0,0,0,,这是代替切嗣？
Dialogue: 0,1:05:15.55,1:05:16.01,Default,,0,0,0,,不
Dialogue: 0,1:05:16.76,1:05:19.10,Default,,0,0,0,,我不是他
Dialogue: 0,1:05:21.31,1:05:22.48,Default,,0,0,0,,但是 我…
Dialogue: 0,1:05:31.78,1:05:33.65,Default,,0,0,0,,士郎 蹲下来
Dialogue: 0,1:05:46.71,1:05:48.46,Default,,0,0,0,,路上小心 士郎
Dialogue: 0,1:05:49.34,1:05:52.76,Default,,0,0,0,,天亮前把樱带回来吧
Dialogue: 0,1:06:10.57,1:06:14.53,Default,,0,0,0,,上面的池子好像有什么特殊的力场
Dialogue: 0,1:06:16.86,1:06:19.03,Default,,0,0,0,,那边的力场是表面的门
Dialogue: 0,1:06:19.78,1:06:21.95,Default,,0,0,0,,要想前往大圣杯…
Dialogue: 0,1:06:27.00,1:06:28.04,Default,,0,0,0,,不是往上走
Dialogue: 0,1:06:28.33,1:06:29.71,Default,,0,0,0,,而是要往下走
Dialogue: 0,1:06:34.76,1:06:35.47,Default,,0,0,0,,往下
Dialogue: 0,1:07:09.54,1:07:10.21,Default,,0,0,0,,士郎
Dialogue: 0,1:07:12.09,1:07:12.59,Default,,0,0,0,,没什么
Dialogue: 0,1:07:13.09,1:07:14.13,Default,,0,0,0,,不要放松警惕
Dialogue: 0,1:07:14.59,1:07:17.47,Default,,0,0,0,,接下来要以自己的性命为重
Dialogue: 0,1:07:37.40,1:07:38.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Saber
Dialogue: 0,1:07:41.91,1:07:42.37,Default,,0,0,0,,凛
Dialogue: 0,1:07:46.87,1:07:47.96,Default,,0,0,0,,原来如此
Dialogue: 0,1:07:51.54,1:07:53.54,Default,,0,0,0,,看来她是认真的
Dialogue: 0,1:08:00.34,1:08:01.18,Default,,0,0,0,,不好意思
Dialogue: 0,1:08:01.51,1:08:02.93,Default,,0,0,0,,我先走一步了
Dialogue: 0,1:08:06.97,1:08:10.64,Default,,0,0,0,,你们如果想救樱 就不要拖太久
Dialogue: 0,1:08:30.71,1:08:31.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Saber
Dialogue: 0,1:08:32.00,1:08:33.83,Default,,0,0,0,,无论如何你都不会让开吧
Dialogue: 0,1:08:34.59,1:08:35.21,Default,,0,0,0,,明知故问
Dialogue: 0,1:08:35.96,1:08:37.59,Default,,0,0,0,,这就是我的职责
Dialogue: 0,1:08:40.42,1:08:43.76,Default,,0,0,0,,我如果用全力 应该能相持两分钟
Dialogue: 0,1:08:44.72,1:08:46.60,Default,,0,0,0,,我来给你制造机会
Dialogue: 0,1:08:49.60,1:08:52.81,Default,,0,0,0,,你按兵不动 不要错过任何机会
Dialogue: 0,1:08:57.78,1:08:58.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Saber
Dialogue: 0,1:08:59.78,1:09:01.74,Default,,0,0,0,,我要在这里消灭你
Dialogue: 0,1:09:03.11,1:09:04.78,Default,,0,0,0,,为了救樱
Dialogue: 0,1:09:08.24,1:09:09.04,Default,,0,0,0,,你很…
Dialogue: 0,1:09:09.62,1:09:10.41,Default,,0,0,0,,碍事
Dialogue: 0,1:10:29.41,1:10:30.28,Default,,0,0,0,,这就是…
Dialogue: 0,1:10:31.06,1:10:31.99,Default,,0,0,0,,大圣杯
Dialogue: 0,1:10:40.88,1:10:43.09,Default,,0,0,0,,你真的没有逃跑 来找我了呢
Dialogue: 0,1:10:49.43,1:10:50.80,Default,,0,0,0,,我想过了
Dialogue: 0,1:10:53.39,1:10:54.06,Default,,0,0,0,,我…
Dialogue: 0,1:10:54.85,1:10:56.85,Default,,0,0,0,,讨厌这个世界
Dialogue: 0,1:10:57.81,1:10:58.48,Default,,0,0,0,,家里也好
Dialogue: 0,1:10:59.02,1:10:59.81,Default,,0,0,0,,姐姐也好
Dialogue: 0,1:11:00.31,1:11:01.23,Default,,0,0,0,,爷爷也好
Dialogue: 0,1:11:01.98,1:11:05.40,Default,,0,0,0,,还有可怜的哥哥和和平度日的城市也好
Dialogue: 0,1:11:06.36,1:11:10.28,Default,,0,0,0,,对我视若无睹的一切都不可饶恕
Dialogue: 0,1:11:11.74,1:11:16.04,Default,,0,0,0,,我也知道把自己的痛苦发泄在别人身上不对
Dialogue: 0,1:11:17.33,1:11:19.46,Default,,0,0,0,,但我变强了
Dialogue: 0,1:11:21.34,1:11:23.71,Default,,0,0,0,,已经没人能阻止我了
Dialogue: 0,1:11:24.63,1:11:25.21,Default,,0,0,0,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,1:11:25.88,1:11:27.63,Default,,0,0,0,,杀人成性了？
Dialogue: 0,1:11:28.68,1:11:32.60,Default,,0,0,0,,没错 Assassin和爷爷都已经不在了
Dialogue: 0,1:11:33.56,1:11:34.18,Default,,0,0,0,,剩下就是…
Dialogue: 0,1:11:34.18,1:11:35.52,Default,,0,0,0,,那士郎呢？
Dialogue: 0,1:11:37.94,1:11:41.98,Default,,0,0,0,,他至今还坚信能救你
Dialogue: 0,1:11:43.64,1:11:47.61,Default,,0,0,0,,我想杀的人 只有他
Dialogue: 0,1:11:48.99,1:11:49.53,Default,,0,0,0,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,1:11:50.24,1:11:52.24,Default,,0,0,0,,看来你早就抛弃了人性
Dialogue: 0,1:11:53.62,1:11:54.91,Default,,0,0,0,,嘴巴真硬
Dialogue: 0,1:11:55.70,1:11:57.79,Default,,0,0,0,,你很羡慕这份力量吧
Dialogue: 0,1:11:58.79,1:12:03.17,Default,,0,0,0,,又想抢走它 只让自己一个人幸福吗
Dialogue: 0,1:12:13.76,1:12:14.68,Default,,0,0,0,,想得美
Dialogue: 0,1:12:15.72,1:12:19.60,Default,,0,0,0,,我能给你的 只有后悔和绝望
Dialogue: 0,1:12:30.53,1:12:32.82,Default,,0,0,0,,就像掉进湖水里的虫子一般
Dialogue: 0,1:12:33.74,1:12:35.78,Default,,0,0,0,,溺死在天之杯中吧
Dialogue: 0,1:13:35.39,1:13:36.09,Default,,0,0,0,,这是…
Dialogue: 0,1:13:48.27,1:13:49.65,Default,,0,0,0,,魔眼的诅咒吗
Dialogue: 0,1:14:02.48,1:14:03.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Rider
Dialogue: 0,1:14:03.91,1:14:05.17,Default,,0,0,0,,有件事我要问你
Dialogue: 0,1:14:05.87,1:14:06.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Saber她…
Dialogue: 0,1:14:07.30,1:14:10.34,Default,,0,0,0,,只有从者才能伤害到她吗
Dialogue: 0,1:14:11.55,1:14:12.05,Default,,0,0,0,,不
Dialogue: 0,1:14:12.59,1:14:15.84,Default,,0,0,0,,被樱吸收的从者完成了受肉
Dialogue: 0,1:14:16.76,1:14:19.05,Default,,0,0,0,,只要是足够强力的礼装 应该就能办到
Dialogue: 0,1:14:21.97,1:14:22.81,Default,,0,0,0,,还有一件
Dialogue: 0,1:14:23.31,1:14:25.14,Default,,0,0,0,,关于作战时的计划
Dialogue: 0,1:14:33.44,1:14:35.95,Default,,0,0,0,,用这个办法确实可以突围
Dialogue: 0,1:14:36.70,1:14:37.24,Default,,0,0,0,,是吧
Dialogue: 0,1:14:38.37,1:14:39.12,Default,,0,0,0,,问题在于…
Dialogue: 0,1:14:39.87,1:14:41.45,Default,,0,0,0,,彼此的信赖是吧
Dialogue: 0,1:14:42.20,1:14:42.87,Default,,0,0,0,,士郎
Dialogue: 0,1:14:45.29,1:14:49.46,Default,,0,0,0,,你就算见到伙伴陷入危机 也能不为所动吗
Dialogue: 0,1:14:52.05,1:14:54.92,Default,,0,0,0,,我要你做到你最不擅长做的事
Dialogue: 0,1:15:09.65,1:15:10.73,Default,,0,0,0,,当然相信
Dialogue: 0,1:15:28.62,1:15:30.46,Default,,0,0,0,,你很在意士郎吗
Dialogue: 0,1:15:31.25,1:15:32.38,Default,,0,0,0,,别想靠近他
Dialogue: 0,1:15:34.09,1:15:36.84,Default,,0,0,0,,因为我背负着他的信任
Dialogue: 0,1:15:38.26,1:15:40.43,Default,,0,0,0,,对了 本来应该是你…
Dialogue: 0,1:15:42.60,1:15:43.64,Default,,0,0,0,,口舌之能
Dialogue: 0,1:17:09.64,1:17:11.31,Default,,0,0,0,,雕虫小技
Dialogue: 0,1:17:16.86,1:17:17.48,Default,,0,0,0,,宝具
Dialogue: 0,1:17:24.24,1:17:24.87,Default,,0,0,0,,来了吗
Dialogue: 0,1:17:36.25,1:17:37.75,Default,,0,0,0,,投影开始
Dialogue: 0,1:17:38.84,1:17:39.59,Default,,0,0,0,,检索
Dialogue: 0,1:17:40.17,1:17:41.01,Default,,0,0,0,,选出
Dialogue: 0,1:17:41.72,1:17:42.59,Default,,0,0,0,,解析
Dialogue: 0,1:17:47.89,1:17:50.72,Default,,0,0,0,,此身为剑所成
Dialogue: 0,1:17:47.89,1:17:50.72,small,,0,0,0,,I am the bone of my sword
Dialogue: 0,1:17:53.77,1:17:54.69,Default,,0,0,0,,炽天覆——
Dialogue: 0,1:17:53.77,1:17:54.69,small,,0,0,0,,Rho-
Dialogue: 0,1:17:55.35,1:17:56.40,Default,,0,0,0,,誓约——
Dialogue: 0,1:17:55.35,1:17:56.40,small,,0,0,0,,Ex-
Dialogue: 0,1:17:59.69,1:18:00.57,Default,,0,0,0,,七重圆环
Dialogue: 0,1:17:59.69,1:18:00.57,small,,0,0,0,,Aias
Dialogue: 0,1:18:02.61,1:18:04.65,Default,,0,0,0,,胜利之剑
Dialogue: 0,1:18:02.61,1:18:04.65,small,,0,0,0,,calibur
Dialogue: 0,1:18:20.55,1:18:21.59,Default,,0,0,0,,骑英之——
Dialogue: 0,1:18:20.55,1:18:21.59,small,,0,0,0,,Bellero-
Dialogue: 0,1:18:24.80,1:18:27.34,Default,,0,0,0,,缰绳
Dialogue: 0,1:18:24.80,1:18:27.34,Default,,0,0,0,,phon
Dialogue: 0,1:19:16.23,1:19:17.14,Default,,0,0,0,,士郎？
Dialogue: 0,1:19:30.66,1:19:31.49,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢你…
Dialogue: 0,1:19:32.41,1:19:35.70,Default,,0,0,0,,你救了我无数次
Dialogue: 0,1:19:58.44,1:19:59.44,Default,,0,0,0,,我先过去了
Dialogue: 0,1:19:59.98,1:20:01.56,Default,,0,0,0,,你能跑了就马上过来
Dialogue: 0,1:20:07.19,1:20:08.24,Default,,0,0,0,,看不出来
Dialogue: 0,1:20:08.95,1:20:10.82,Default,,0,0,0,,你还真会使唤人
Dialogue: 0,1:20:57.58,1:20:58.54,Default,,0,0,0,,去死
Dialogue: 0,1:21:29.15,1:21:29.73,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么会…
Dialogue: 0,1:21:34.95,1:21:35.82,Default,,0,0,0,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,1:21:37.24,1:21:38.62,Default,,0,0,0,,没有为什么
Dialogue: 0,1:21:39.79,1:21:42.25,Default,,0,0,0,,这不过是单纯的以力制胜罢了
Dialogue: 0,1:21:44.25,1:21:44.96,Default,,0,0,0,,那…
Dialogue: 0,1:21:45.58,1:21:47.04,Default,,0,0,0,,那东西里面有什么
Dialogue: 0,1:21:47.88,1:21:49.55,Default,,0,0,0,,你不知道吗 樱
Dialogue: 0,1:21:50.62,1:21:54.30,Default,,0,0,0,,这是远坂家传承的宝石剑泽尔里奇
Dialogue: 0,1:21:50.62,1:21:54.30,small,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1260,995)}Zelretch
Dialogue: 0,1:21:55.14,1:22:00.52,Default,,0,0,0,,它能连结无限并列的平行世界以流出魔力
Dialogue: 0,1:22:03.73,1:22:05.94,Default,,0,0,0,,泽尔…里奇？
Dialogue: 0,1:22:08.48,1:22:11.99,Default,,0,0,0,,真是服了你 连泽尔里奇都没听说过吗
Dialogue: 0,1:22:13.61,1:22:14.65,Default,,0,0,0,,你敢小看我
Dialogue: 0,1:22:19.08,1:22:20.99,Default,,0,0,0,,不管你储存了多少魔力
Dialogue: 0,1:22:21.79,1:22:25.83,Default,,0,0,0,,你一次放出魔力的量 和我并没有太大的区别
Dialogue: 0,1:22:26.88,1:22:31.25,Default,,0,0,0,,所以我每次只要准备好和你相当的魔力就好
Dialogue: 0,1:22:37.47,1:22:39.89,Default,,0,0,0,,就算你有用之不竭的魔力池
Dialogue: 0,1:22:40.56,1:22:42.97,Default,,0,0,0,,也不过是暴殄天物而已
Dialogue: 0,1:22:53.40,1:22:54.40,Default,,0,0,0,,不公平
Dialogue: 0,1:22:57.53,1:22:58.62,Default,,0,0,0,,不公平
Dialogue: 0,1:23:06.58,1:23:07.54,Default,,0,0,0,,这不公平
Dialogue: 0,1:23:29.90,1:23:33.19,Default,,0,0,0,,被力量冲昏的头脑是不是清醒点了
Dialogue: 0,1:23:36.82,1:23:37.74,Default,,0,0,0,,这样…
Dialogue: 0,1:23:38.61,1:23:39.74,Default,,0,0,0,,根本就不公平
Dialogue: 0,1:23:40.82,1:23:42.10,Default,,0,0,0,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,1:23:42.53,1:23:43.91,Default,,0,0,0,,同样是姐妹
Dialogue: 0,1:23:44.45,1:23:47.41,Default,,0,0,0,,为什么只有我一直受到非人的对待
Dialogue: 0,1:23:48.62,1:23:51.04,Default,,0,0,0,,身上被刻下玛奇里的魔术
Dialogue: 0,1:23:51.58,1:23:53.59,Default,,0,0,0,,连吃的都是毒物
Dialogue: 0,1:23:54.59,1:23:58.26,Default,,0,0,0,,以至于我对食物只有恐惧和疼痛的回忆
Dialogue: 0,1:23:59.26,1:24:03.55,Default,,0,0,0,,在虫仓 就连吸一口气都要获得许可
Dialogue: 0,1:24:04.72,1:24:10.44,Default,,0,0,0,,我一哭他们就会愉快地践踏我的身体
Dialogue: 0,1:24:11.81,1:24:15.19,Default,,0,0,0,,就在我痛苦的时候 姐姐却一直都是这么耀眼
Dialogue: 0,1:24:15.86,1:24:17.99,Default,,0,0,0,,在无忧无虑的环境中长大
Dialogue: 0,1:24:18.44,1:24:21.99,Default,,0,0,0,,我好恨 好想赢
Dialogue: 0,1:24:23.37,1:24:27.75,Default,,0,0,0,,哪怕一次也好 我多希望姐姐能够夸夸我
Dialogue: 0,1:24:29.12,1:24:32.58,Default,,0,0,0,,我原本就是远坂家的孩子
Dialogue: 0,1:24:33.42,1:24:36.17,Default,,0,0,0,,所以我一直相信着
Dialogue: 0,1:24:36.80,1:24:38.13,Default,,0,0,0,,有一天姐姐会来救我
Dialogue: 0,1:24:39.26,1:24:42.43,Default,,0,0,0,,然而你没有
Dialogue: 0,1:24:43.76,1:24:45.51,Default,,0,0,0,,这可是11年啊
Dialogue: 0,1:24:46.81,1:24:48.31,Default,,0,0,0,,换谁都会疯了吧
Dialogue: 0,1:24:49.68,1:24:51.94,Default,,0,0,0,,但这是我的错吗
Dialogue: 0,1:24:53.06,1:24:56.86,Default,,0,0,0,,我每天都好痛好痛好痛好痛
Dialogue: 0,1:24:58.23,1:25:00.36,Default,,0,0,0,,又不是我想变成这样的
Dialogue: 0,1:25:02.53,1:25:05.45,Default,,0,0,0,,我也没有任何办法啊
Dialogue: 0,1:25:09.75,1:25:11.54,Default,,0,0,0,,然后呢
Dialogue: 0,1:25:12.54,1:25:13.08,Default,,0,0,0,,那又怎样
Dialogue: 0,1:25:19.42,1:25:22.93,Default,,0,0,0,,你现在不是不痛了吗
Dialogue: 0,1:25:25.55,1:25:26.60,Default,,0,0,0,,什…
Dialogue: 0,1:25:27.60,1:25:30.22,Default,,0,0,0,,就是因为你老是这个样子
Dialogue: 0,1:25:31.64,1:25:34.94,Default,,0,0,0,,我不是很能理解他人的痛苦
Dialogue: 0,1:25:36.77,1:25:40.69,Default,,0,0,0,,所以无论你每天过得有多么凄惨
Dialogue: 0,1:25:41.53,1:25:43.28,Default,,0,0,0,,我也不会想去理解
Dialogue: 0,1:25:46.99,1:25:47.87,Default,,0,0,0,,但是 樱
Dialogue: 0,1:25:49.24,1:25:51.37,Default,,0,0,0,,就算我再后知后觉
Dialogue: 0,1:25:52.96,1:25:55.38,Default,,0,0,0,,我也从来没有觉得…
Dialogue: 0,1:25:57.17,1:25:59.46,Default,,0,0,0,,自己是被眷顾的
Dialogue: 0,1:26:08.35,1:26:09.51,Default,,0,0,0,,竟敢…
Dialogue: 0,1:26:12.43,1:26:15.35,Default,,0,0,0,,竟敢说出这种话
Dialogue: 0,1:26:17.77,1:26:18.52,Default,,0,0,0,,樱
Dialogue: 0,1:26:27.49,1:26:28.53,Default,,0,0,0,,万象崩坏
Dialogue: 0,1:26:27.49,1:26:28.53,small,,0,0,0,,Welt Ende
Dialogue: 0,1:27:24.17,1:27:25.09,Default,,0,0,0,,这样不行
Dialogue: 0,1:27:39.94,1:27:41.69,Default,,0,0,0,,姐…姐？
Dialogue: 0,1:27:50.41,1:27:52.24,Default,,0,0,0,,我好傻
Dialogue: 0,1:27:53.45,1:27:57.79,Default,,0,0,0,,但是我见不得努力的人得不到回报
Dialogue: 0,1:27:58.71,1:28:03.75,Default,,0,0,0,,更何况我喜欢你 希望能经常看见你笑
Dialogue: 0,1:28:08.47,1:28:10.55,Default,,0,0,0,,我一直相信只要自己承受多一点
Dialogue: 0,1:28:11.34,1:28:14.47,Default,,0,0,0,,你就能过得轻松一些
Dialogue: 0,1:28:16.72,1:28:20.02,Default,,0,0,0,,我也没资格说士郎啊
Dialogue: 0,1:28:24.69,1:28:26.53,Default,,0,0,0,,看着眼前的你
Dialogue: 0,1:28:26.53,1:28:28.53,Default,,0,0,0,,我就明白自己下不了手
Dialogue: 0,1:28:30.40,1:28:31.24,Default,,0,0,0,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,1:28:32.66,1:28:34.08,Default,,0,0,0,,当姐姐的还这么任性
Dialogue: 0,1:28:35.45,1:28:36.62,Default,,0,0,0,,还有…
Dialogue: 0,1:28:37.50,1:28:38.45,Default,,0,0,0,,这个缎带…
Dialogue: 0,1:28:39.54,1:28:41.33,Default,,0,0,0,,看到你一直绑着…
Dialogue: 0,1:28:42.21,1:28:43.38,Default,,0,0,0,,我好开心…
Dialogue: 0,1:29:10.95,1:29:11.90,Default,,0,0,0,,我有
Dialogue: 0,1:29:14.87,1:29:17.91,Default,,0,0,0,,我明明也有…
Dialogue: 0,1:29:21.50,1:29:22.71,Default,,0,0,0,,却被我…
Dialogue: 0,1:29:24.29,1:29:26.25,Default,,0,0,0,,亲手给毁了
Dialogue: 0,1:30:01.54,1:30:02.20,Default,,0,0,0,,前…
Dialogue: 0,1:30:02.87,1:30:03.54,Default,,0,0,0,,辈
Dialogue: 0,1:30:20.85,1:30:21.64,Default,,0,0,0,,是我…
Dialogue: 0,1:30:23.14,1:30:25.04,Default,,0,0,0,,是我…杀的
Dialogue: 0,1:30:26.15,1:30:28.19,Default,,0,0,0,,是我…把姐姐
Dialogue: 0,1:30:29.86,1:30:33.82,Default,,0,0,0,,明明她一直都叫我不要认输
Dialogue: 0,1:30:35.49,1:30:36.28,Default,,0,0,0,,不要
Dialogue: 0,1:30:37.28,1:30:39.45,Default,,0,0,0,,不能再继续下去了
Dialogue: 0,1:30:44.91,1:30:46.25,Default,,0,0,0,,是远坂…
Dialogue: 0,1:30:47.42,1:30:48.42,Default,,0,0,0,,赢了啊
Dialogue: 0,1:30:51.80,1:30:52.55,Default,,0,0,0,,樱
Dialogue: 0,1:30:53.42,1:30:54.80,Default,,0,0,0,,远坂还没死
Dialogue: 0,1:30:57.26,1:30:58.47,Default,,0,0,0,,她还有救
Dialogue: 0,1:30:59.26,1:31:00.97,Default,,0,0,0,,我们还能救她
Dialogue: 0,1:31:11.73,1:31:12.65,Default,,0,0,0,,不行
Dialogue: 0,1:31:12.65,1:31:13.90,Default,,0,0,0,,快走 前辈
Dialogue: 0,1:31:23.20,1:31:24.50,Default,,0,0,0,,不 不是…
Dialogue: 0,1:31:25.04,1:31:26.54,Default,,0,0,0,,不是的 前辈
Dialogue: 0,1:31:27.00,1:31:27.71,Default,,0,0,0,,不是我…
Dialogue: 0,1:31:28.17,1:31:29.00,Default,,0,0,0,,我知道
Dialogue: 0,1:31:29.75,1:31:32.21,Default,,0,0,0,,死到临头这孩子还不肯悔改
Dialogue: 0,1:31:48.60,1:31:51.48,Default,,0,0,0,,前辈 带上姐姐快走
Dialogue: 0,1:32:12.38,1:32:13.04,Default,,0,0,0,,不行
Dialogue: 0,1:32:14.00,1:32:15.30,Default,,0,0,0,,压制不住
Dialogue: 0,1:32:16.17,1:32:17.88,Default,,0,0,0,,快逃 前辈
Dialogue: 0,1:32:23.51,1:32:24.68,Default,,0,0,0,,住手
Dialogue: 0,1:32:25.81,1:32:28.23,Default,,0,0,0,,我会去死的
Dialogue: 0,1:32:29.14,1:32:32.10,Default,,0,0,0,,我会一个人乖乖去死的
Dialogue: 0,1:32:40.82,1:32:42.16,Default,,0,0,0,,为什么要救我
Dialogue: 0,1:32:43.28,1:32:44.91,Default,,0,0,0,,我已经没救了
Dialogue: 0,1:32:45.78,1:32:48.75,Default,,0,0,0,,不 我没资格被救
Dialogue: 0,1:32:58.26,1:32:59.00,Default,,0,0,0,,能救
Dialogue: 0,1:33:13.65,1:33:14.31,Default,,0,0,0,,樱
Dialogue: 0,1:33:24.57,1:33:25.45,Default,,0,0,0,,你看
Dialogue: 0,1:33:26.24,1:33:28.24,Default,,0,0,0,,你看到了吧 前辈
Dialogue: 0,1:33:29.91,1:33:32.33,Default,,0,0,0,,我就是这种人
Dialogue: 0,1:33:33.24,1:33:33.78,Default,,0,0,0,,所以
Dialogue: 0,1:33:43.59,1:33:46.72,Default,,0,0,0,,我杀了很多人
Dialogue: 0,1:33:48.01,1:33:50.52,Default,,0,0,0,,哥哥 爷爷
Dialogue: 0,1:33:51.98,1:33:53.88,Default,,0,0,0,,还有姐姐
Dialogue: 0,1:33:55.10,1:33:55.98,Default,,0,0,0,,就算这样
Dialogue: 0,1:33:56.77,1:34:00.78,Default,,0,0,0,,就算这样你还要我继续活下去吗
Dialogue: 0,1:34:00.78,1:34:01.57,Default,,0,0,0,,没错
Dialogue: 0,1:34:02.44,1:34:03.45,Default,,0,0,0,,这是当然的
Dialogue: 0,1:34:04.78,1:34:07.78,Default,,0,0,0,,既然夺走了生命 就要负起责任
Dialogue: 0,1:34:14.87,1:34:16.75,Default,,0,0,0,,前…辈
Dialogue: 0,1:34:26.68,1:34:28.05,Default,,0,0,0,,你有什么罪恶
Dialogue: 0,1:34:28.72,1:34:30.01,Default,,0,0,0,,你要受多重的惩罚
Dialogue: 0,1:34:30.89,1:34:32.27,Default,,0,0,0,,这些我一无所知
Dialogue: 0,1:34:33.64,1:34:34.60,Default,,0,0,0,,但是我会保护你
Dialogue: 0,1:34:35.60,1:34:40.19,Default,,0,0,0,,今后我会从一切问责声中保护你
Dialogue: 0,1:34:41.36,1:34:43.94,Default,,0,0,0,,哪怕这是伪善也好
Dialogue: 0,1:34:45.32,1:34:47.41,Default,,0,0,0,,我也要将喜欢的人保护到底
Dialogue: 0,1:34:51.04,1:34:53.08,Default,,0,0,0,,投影 开始
Dialogue: 0,1:34:51.04,1:34:53.08,small,,0,0,0,,Trace On
Dialogue: 0,1:34:57.71,1:34:58.75,Default,,0,0,0,,这是惩罚
Dialogue: 0,1:35:01.17,1:35:02.59,Default,,0,0,0,,这一下会很痛
Dialogue: 0,1:35:03.42,1:35:04.80,Default,,0,0,0,,咬紧牙关
Dialogue: 0,1:35:16.10,1:35:16.69,Default,,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,1:35:27.53,1:35:29.03,Default,,0,0,0,,回家吧 樱
Dialogue: 0,1:35:30.20,1:35:32.12,Default,,0,0,0,,不要再和那种东西扯上关系了
Dialogue: 0,1:36:37.93,1:36:38.85,Default,,0,0,0,,无法阻止…
Dialogue: 0,1:36:39.77,1:36:40.35,Default,,0,0,0,,吗
Dialogue: 0,1:37:03.00,1:37:03.71,Default,,0,0,0,,士郎
Dialogue: 0,1:37:08.05,1:37:08.80,Default,,0,0,0,,是你啊
Dialogue: 0,1:37:09.55,1:37:10.42,Default,,0,0,0,,来得正好
Dialogue: 0,1:37:11.13,1:37:13.72,Default,,0,0,0,,能拜托你 带着樱和下面的远坂…
Dialogue: 0,1:37:14.64,1:37:16.18,Default,,0,0,0,,离开这里吗
Dialogue: 0,1:37:17.18,1:37:17.72,Default,,0,0,0,,那个…
Dialogue: 0,1:37:18.85,1:37:19.22,Default,,0,0,0,,R…
Dialogue: 0,1:37:20.31,1:37:20.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Ri…
Dialogue: 0,1:37:24.06,1:37:25.11,Default,,0,0,0,,我明白了
Dialogue: 0,1:37:30.15,1:37:30.86,Default,,0,0,0,,拜托了
Dialogue: 0,1:37:32.61,1:37:32.91,Default,,0,0,0,,还…
Dialogue: 0,1:37:33.61,1:37:34.16,Default,,0,0,0,,还有
Dialogue: 0,1:37:36.45,1:37:37.12,Default,,0,0,0,,把这个…
Dialogue: 0,1:37:38.79,1:37:39.62,Default,,0,0,0,,交给樱
Dialogue: 0,1:37:42.71,1:37:45.04,Default,,0,0,0,,这个还是你自己…
Dialogue: 0,1:37:51.30,1:37:51.84,Default,,0,0,0,,不
Dialogue: 0,1:37:53.01,1:37:53.93,Default,,0,0,0,,祝你凯旋归来
Dialogue: 0,1:38:35.76,1:38:36.64,Default,,0,0,0,,言峰…
Dialogue: 0,1:38:37.47,1:38:38.10,Default,,0,0,0,,绮礼
Dialogue: 0,1:38:40.76,1:38:41.52,Default,,0,0,0,,看来…
Dialogue: 0,1:38:42.02,1:38:44.89,Default,,0,0,0,,我们都苟延残喘地活了下来了
Dialogue: 0,1:38:46.02,1:38:46.73,Default,,0,0,0,,卫宫…
Dialogue: 0,1:38:47.40,1:38:48.15,Default,,0,0,0,,士郎
Dialogue: 0,1:38:52.94,1:38:54.44,Default,,0,0,0,,就算把它放出来了
Dialogue: 0,1:38:55.40,1:38:57.20,Default,,0,0,0,,你的愿望也不会实现
Dialogue: 0,1:38:58.28,1:38:59.45,Default,,0,0,0,,能实现
Dialogue: 0,1:39:00.45,1:39:03.12,Default,,0,0,0,,我的目的只有一个
Dialogue: 0,1:39:03.75,1:39:07.00,Default,,0,0,0,,就是让这个诅咒诞生在这个世上
Dialogue: 0,1:39:07.88,1:39:08.75,Default,,0,0,0,,为什么…
Dialogue: 0,1:39:09.50,1:39:11.09,Default,,0,0,0,,为什么要如此保护它
Dialogue: 0,1:39:11.88,1:39:14.26,Default,,0,0,0,,他根本就是恶本身
Dialogue: 0,1:39:15.09,1:39:16.72,Default,,0,0,0,,它还不是恶
Dialogue: 0,1:39:17.80,1:39:18.97,Default,,0,0,0,,但也不是善
Dialogue: 0,1:39:21.01,1:39:25.10,Default,,0,0,0,,人类是从无开始学习什么是正确的
Dialogue: 0,1:39:26.18,1:39:27.73,Default,,0,0,0,,开始是无
Dialogue: 0,1:39:29.73,1:39:33.44,Default,,0,0,0,,只有存在这一个事实
Dialogue: 0,1:39:39.95,1:39:42.03,Default,,0,0,0,,如果人们要怪罪它
Dialogue: 0,1:39:42.41,1:39:48.67,Default,,0,0,0,,责任也在孕育它环境 和他们自身
Dialogue: 0,1:39:50.08,1:39:52.63,Default,,0,0,0,,如果这个生命希望被孵化
Dialogue: 0,1:39:53.17,1:39:55.84,Default,,0,0,0,,那么我去孵化它 就是爱
Dialogue: 0,1:39:57.51,1:39:58.68,Default,,0,0,0,,这算什么爱
Dialogue: 0,1:40:00.05,1:40:03.31,Default,,0,0,0,,对我来说就是 卫宫士郎
Dialogue: 0,1:40:04.81,1:40:08.31,Default,,0,0,0,,就像你会从他人的幸福中感受至高的快乐
Dialogue: 0,1:40:09.27,1:40:10.15,Default,,0,0,0,,而我只是…
Dialogue: 0,1:40:10.85,1:40:14.11,Default,,0,0,0,,从他人的不幸中感受到罢了
Dialogue: 0,1:40:42.64,1:40:44.51,Default,,0,0,0,,真是棘手的身体
Dialogue: 0,1:40:45.10,1:40:47.35,Default,,0,0,0,,反而是打的人要搭上性命
Dialogue: 0,1:41:02.28,1:41:06.54,Default,,0,0,0,,你说 杀人这种行为是恶
Dialogue: 0,1:41:07.20,1:41:10.75,Default,,0,0,0,,那想要保护间桐樱的你又怎样
Dialogue: 0,1:41:15.88,1:41:18.38,Default,,0,0,0,,人类就是这样
Dialogue: 0,1:41:19.17,1:41:21.93,Default,,0,0,0,,恶人会闹着玩地向你释出善意
Dialogue: 0,1:41:22.34,1:41:25.35,Default,,0,0,0,,圣人也会一时昏头犯下罪行
Dialogue: 0,1:41:26.10,1:41:29.93,Default,,0,0,0,,就是这种矛盾 造就了人类
Dialogue: 0,1:41:30.73,1:41:35.44,Default,,0,0,0,,所谓活着 就是同时孕育善恶两面
Dialogue: 0,1:41:43.24,1:41:43.95,Default,,0,0,0,,但是
Dialogue: 0,1:41:44.32,1:41:46.99,Default,,0,0,0,,它从开始就以杀为生
Dialogue: 0,1:41:48.62,1:41:49.49,Default,,0,0,0,,没错
Dialogue: 0,1:41:49.95,1:41:53.21,Default,,0,0,0,,可它自己是怎么想的
Dialogue: 0,1:41:53.58,1:41:55.17,Default,,0,0,0,,还没人知道
Dialogue: 0,1:41:56.08,1:41:58.46,Default,,0,0,0,,它究竟会感叹自己是恶的化身
Dialogue: 0,1:41:58.46,1:41:59.84,Default,,0,0,0,,还是认为自己在行善
Dialogue: 0,1:42:00.21,1:42:02.88,Default,,0,0,0,,只要它对人们对它的期待
Dialogue: 0,1:42:02.88,1:42:06.34,Default,,0,0,0,,以及自身的机能深信不疑
Dialogue: 0,1:42:06.68,1:42:08.01,Default,,0,0,0,,那就不是恶
Dialogue: 0,1:42:11.27,1:42:12.89,Default,,0,0,0,,只要它诞生
Dialogue: 0,1:42:13.44,1:42:16.10,Default,,0,0,0,,就能如众人所愿 杀尽一切事物
Dialogue: 0,1:42:17.02,1:42:19.86,Default,,0,0,0,,如果全世界只剩下一个人
Dialogue: 0,1:42:20.32,1:42:23.07,Default,,0,0,0,,那它会放过自己吗
Dialogue: 0,1:42:25.20,1:42:26.20,Default,,0,0,0,,我就是…
Dialogue: 0,1:42:26.87,1:42:28.45,Default,,0,0,0,,想知道这个
Dialogue: 0,1:42:32.00,1:42:33.96,Default,,0,0,0,,就为了这种事
Dialogue: 0,1:42:35.37,1:42:36.46,Default,,0,0,0,,你就要
Dialogue: 0,1:42:49.68,1:42:50.60,Default,,0,0,0,,没错
Dialogue: 0,1:42:51.35,1:42:53.81,Default,,0,0,0,,这就是我的目的
Dialogue: 0,1:42:54.14,1:42:55.31,Default,,0,0,0,,卫宫士郎
Dialogue: 0,1:42:56.44,1:42:59.77,Default,,0,0,0,,我和不求实现自己愿望的你
Dialogue: 0,1:43:00.52,1:43:02.23,Default,,0,0,0,,是最极端的对立
Dialogue: 0,1:43:03.49,1:43:03.99,Default,,0,0,0,,但是
Dialogue: 0,1:43:04.61,1:43:06.36,Default,,0,0,0,,我们愿望的本质是相同的
Dialogue: 0,1:43:29.85,1:43:30.80,Default,,0,0,0,,这样啊
Dialogue: 0,1:43:31.89,1:43:35.68,Default,,0,0,0,,我们都认为自己是罪人
Dialogue: 0,1:43:36.56,1:43:38.23,Default,,0,0,0,,为了摆脱这种想法
Dialogue: 0,1:43:38.65,1:43:40.90,Default,,0,0,0,,我们才会将自己的活法贯彻始终
Dialogue: 0,1:43:46.24,1:43:47.57,Default,,0,0,0,,这也难怪
Dialogue: 0,1:43:48.49,1:43:49.41,Default,,0,0,0,,不会退让
Dialogue: 0,1:43:51.91,1:43:55.45,Default,,0,0,0,,坦白说 这也是迁怒于人
Dialogue: 0,1:43:56.62,1:43:59.46,Default,,0,0,0,,我很羡慕你们
Dialogue: 0,1:44:01.00,1:44:01.84,Default,,0,0,0,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,1:44:02.88,1:44:04.84,Default,,0,0,0,,害你浪费时间了
Dialogue: 0,1:44:05.92,1:44:06.76,Default,,0,0,0,,无所谓
Dialogue: 0,1:44:08.22,1:44:11.05,Default,,0,0,0,,我们的时间都不多了
Dialogue: 0,1:44:25.86,1:44:27.53,Default,,0,0,0,,我不想死
Dialogue: 0,1:44:28.32,1:44:29.78,Default,,0,0,0,,我不想死
Dialogue: 0,1:44:30.74,1:44:32.41,Default,,0,0,0,,我不想死
Dialogue: 0,1:44:33.24,1:44:34.83,Default,,0,0,0,,我不想…
Dialogue: 0,1:44:39.71,1:44:41.75,Default,,0,0,0,,试问 我的仇敌
Dialogue: 0,1:44:43.21,1:44:45.88,Default,,0,0,0,,你为什么不想死
Dialogue: 0,1:44:55.18,1:44:57.85,Default,,0,0,0,,为了根绝一切罪恶
Dialogue: 0,1:44:58.31,1:45:01.35,Default,,0,0,0,,你们需要奇迹
Dialogue: 0,1:45:04.81,1:45:06.90,Default,,0,0,0,,人类的世界没有救赎
Dialogue: 0,1:45:07.44,1:45:11.11,Default,,0,0,0,,既然生而为人无法与罪恶切割
Dialogue: 0,1:45:14.70,1:45:15.91,Default,,0,0,0,,既然理想乡
Dialogue: 0,1:45:16.45,1:45:20.41,Default,,0,0,0,,是人类之身无法抵达的地点
Dialogue: 0,1:45:21.92,1:45:23.54,Default,,0,0,0,,那就去追求
Dialogue: 0,1:45:24.54,1:45:26.96,Default,,0,0,0,,足以超越人类的全新模样
Dialogue: 0,1:45:28.55,1:45:32.72,Default,,0,0,0,,正是 为除世间万恶
Dialogue: 0,1:45:33.93,1:45:34.68,Default,,0,0,0,,吾等…
Dialogue: 0,1:45:35.80,1:45:38.93,Default,,0,0,0,,愿以吾身付诸此愿
Dialogue: 0,1:45:43.52,1:45:45.40,Default,,0,0,0,,五百多年了
Dialogue: 0,1:45:45.40,1:45:49.57,Default,,0,0,0,,回想起来 这夙愿不过也是转瞬之间
Dialogue: 0,1:45:55.78,1:45:58.49,Default,,0,0,0,,明明就差一步了
Dialogue: 0,1:46:14.43,1:46:15.39,Default,,0,0,0,,没想到
Dialogue: 0,1:46:16.47,1:46:18.76,Default,,0,0,0,,我会单纯输在时间上
Dialogue: 0,1:46:26.40,1:46:28.61,Default,,0,0,0,,你是最后的御主
Dialogue: 0,1:46:29.61,1:46:32.15,Default,,0,0,0,,去尽你最后的责任吧
Dialogue: 0,1:47:01.97,1:47:02.81,Default,,0,0,0,,这样…
Dialogue: 0,1:47:03.89,1:47:05.39,Default,,0,0,0,,这样就结束了
Dialogue: 0,1:47:06.73,1:47:07.65,Default,,0,0,0,,要用投影
Dialogue: 0,1:47:19.87,1:47:20.91,Default,,0,0,0,,这样…
Dialogue: 0,1:47:22.95,1:47:23.70,Default,,0,0,0,,真的…
Dialogue: 0,1:47:24.62,1:47:25.41,Default,,0,0,0,,好吗
Dialogue: 0,1:47:34.59,1:47:36.34,Default,,0,0,0,,我是不会让士郎死的
Dialogue: 0,1:47:45.93,1:47:48.23,Default,,0,0,0,,这扇门由我来关上
Dialogue: 0,1:47:49.90,1:47:50.73,Default,,0,0,0,,士郎你…
Dialogue: 0,1:47:51.52,1:47:52.40,Default,,0,0,0,,想活下去吗
Dialogue: 0,1:47:53.32,1:47:55.19,Default,,0,0,0,,无论是成为怎样的生命
Dialogue: 0,1:47:57.11,1:47:58.99,Default,,0,0,0,,无论是以怎样的形态
Dialogue: 0,1:48:03.03,1:48:04.29,Default,,0,0,0,,你也想活下去吗
Dialogue: 0,1:48:08.21,1:48:09.75,Default,,0,0,0,,不行…
Dialogue: 0,1:48:10.88,1:48:12.17,Default,,0,0,0,,别去…
Dialogue: 0,1:48:13.04,1:48:14.13,Default,,0,0,0,,那东西…
Dialogue: 0,1:48:14.80,1:48:15.34,Default,,0,0,0,,由我…
Dialogue: 0,1:48:16.13,1:48:18.43,Default,,0,0,0,,来带走
Dialogue: 0,1:48:21.39,1:48:22.39,Default,,0,0,0,,想活下去吗
Dialogue: 0,1:48:34.40,1:48:35.19,Default,,0,0,0,,想…
Dialogue: 0,1:48:37.28,1:48:39.48,Default,,0,0,0,,我想…活下去
Dialogue: 0,1:48:42.57,1:48:43.66,Default,,0,0,0,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,1:48:48.87,1:48:49.83,Default,,0,0,0,,不行…
Dialogue: 0,1:48:51.67,1:48:52.58,Default,,0,0,0,,回来
Dialogue: 0,1:48:54.34,1:48:55.88,Default,,0,0,0,,让你看一个奇迹
Dialogue: 0,1:48:57.01,1:48:58.67,Default,,0,0,0,,这次真的很厉害
Dialogue: 0,1:48:59.72,1:49:03.51,Default,,0,0,0,,毕竟 这是真正的魔法
Dialogue: 0,1:49:04.72,1:49:05.56,Default,,0,0,0,,这种事…
Dialogue: 0,1:49:05.93,1:49:06.89,Default,,0,0,0,,无所谓…
Dialogue: 0,1:49:07.72,1:49:09.31,Default,,0,0,0,,别说了 快回来
Dialogue: 0,1:49:11.44,1:49:11.94,Default,,0,0,0,,可恶
Dialogue: 0,1:49:12.81,1:49:13.73,Default,,0,0,0,,名字…
Dialogue: 0,1:49:14.56,1:49:15.57,Default,,0,0,0,,想不起名字…
Dialogue: 0,1:49:21.03,1:49:23.82,Default,,0,0,0,,兄长就应该要保护好自己的妹妹 对吗
Dialogue: 0,1:49:30.21,1:49:30.75,Default,,0,0,0,,没错
Dialogue: 0,1:49:31.87,1:49:34.00,Default,,0,0,0,,我可是你的姐姐呀
Dialogue: 0,1:49:35.67,1:49:39.05,Default,,0,0,0,,那我就应该保护好自己的弟弟
Dialogue: 0,1:49:42.01,1:49:42.93,Default,,0,0,0,,伊莉雅
Dialogue: 0,1:49:49.39,1:49:49.97,Default,,0,0,0,,伊莉雅
Dialogue: 0,1:49:50.85,1:49:51.56,Default,,0,0,0,,伊莉雅
Dialogue: 0,1:49:52.35,1:49:53.10,Default,,0,0,0,,伊莉雅
Dialogue: 0,1:49:53.56,1:49:54.27,Default,,0,0,0,,伊莉雅
Dialogue: 0,1:49:54.69,1:49:55.44,Default,,0,0,0,,伊莉雅
Dialogue: 0,1:49:55.90,1:49:56.86,Default,,0,0,0,,伊莉雅
Dialogue: 0,1:49:57.90,1:49:59.94,Default,,0,0,0,,伊莉雅
Dialogue: 0,1:51:57.27,1:51:58.19,Default,,0,0,0,,前…
Dialogue: 0,1:51:59.10,1:51:59.81,Default,,0,0,0,,辈…
Dialogue: 0,1:52:34.76,1:52:36.81,Default,,0,0,0,,不愧是下届部长
Dialogue: 0,1:52:37.48,1:52:39.69,Default,,0,0,0,,看来能安心隐退了
Dialogue: 0,1:52:48.40,1:52:50.95,Default,,0,0,0,,他到底什么时候回来呢
Dialogue: 0,1:53:08.55,1:53:11.43,Default,,0,0,0,,在这片土地上发生的圣杯战争结束了
Dialogue: 0,1:53:13.34,1:53:17.14,Default,,0,0,0,,大圣杯的崩坏 为一切画下了句点
Dialogue: 0,1:53:19.35,1:53:20.89,Default,,0,0,0,,为了收拾残局
Dialogue: 0,1:53:20.89,1:53:23.86,Default,,0,0,0,,我四处奔波 一边忙着应付魔术协会
Dialogue: 0,1:53:23.86,1:53:25.73,Default,,0,0,0,,一边等待着樱康复归来
Dialogue: 0,1:53:28.61,1:53:32.41,Default,,0,0,0,,然后现在 我和樱并肩走着
Dialogue: 0,1:53:34.16,1:53:36.83,Default,,0,0,0,,就像是想要找回那错过的十一年的时光
Dialogue: 0,1:53:37.83,1:53:41.33,Default,,0,0,0,,随着时间的流转 我与樱迈步向前
Dialogue: 0,1:53:43.42,1:53:44.04,Default,,0,0,0,,没错
Dialogue: 0,1:53:45.00,1:53:46.96,Default,,0,0,0,,这是他不在的时光
Dialogue: 0,1:53:48.76,1:53:50.34,Default,,0,0,0,,因为卫宫士郎的身体
Dialogue: 0,1:53:50.92,1:53:52.51,Default,,0,0,0,,已经消失不见了
Dialogue: 0,1:54:34.88,1:54:35.55,Default,,0,0,0,,樱
Dialogue: 0,1:54:36.80,1:54:38.22,Default,,0,0,0,,凛回来了
Dialogue: 0,1:54:41.52,1:54:42.39,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢你
Dialogue: 0,1:54:43.39,1:54:44.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Rider
Dialogue: 0,1:54:48.69,1:54:50.69,Default,,0,0,0,,樱 最近还好吗
Dialogue: 0,1:54:52.15,1:54:52.69,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,1:54:53.40,1:54:54.90,Default,,0,0,0,,慢慢地
Dialogue: 0,1:54:55.53,1:54:59.24,Default,,0,0,0,,我已经可以坦率地接受许多事了
Dialogue: 0,1:55:00.64,1:55:04.79,Default,,0,0,0,,我明白了 输给罪恶感就是逃避
Dialogue: 0,1:55:14.59,1:55:15.72,Default,,0,0,0,,改变的事物
Dialogue: 0,1:55:16.80,1:55:18.55,Default,,0,0,0,,必须改变的事物
Dialogue: 0,1:55:20.68,1:55:23.06,Default,,0,0,0,,究竟怎样才称得上是改变
Dialogue: 0,1:55:24.81,1:55:28.81,Default,,0,0,0,,我仍然在懵懂中寻找着答案
Dialogue: 0,1:55:31.82,1:55:32.36,Default,,0,0,0,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,1:56:01.47,1:56:03.72,Default,,0,0,0,,在这个瞬息万变的世界上
Dialogue: 0,1:56:07.94,1:56:09.94,Default,,0,0,0,,依然有着一如往昔的事物…
Dialogue: 0,1:56:28.25,1:56:30.42,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么了 樱
Dialogue: 0,1:56:36.96,1:56:37.59,Default,,0,0,0,,没什么
Dialogue: 0,1:56:41.39,1:56:42.47,Default,,0,0,0,,快 我们走吧
Dialogue: 0,1:56:43.01,1:56:45.51,Default,,0,0,0,,真是的 瞧把你急的
Dialogue: 0,1:56:47.10,1:56:47.48,Default,,0,0,0,,樱
